{Rf'8cI pf\tc6 \qf*Kqf* f*4RpKeI qe^R6 \fcfKqeI \6KSM4 'MRep6 fppR6 \M9f6 f46*Kf5I tMcfKf'p 'M\\R*fKI efp8 fppR6 6@tcqf* *696e p'f6*KfpK 5Me6f^* '6*K6e cfKKc6 eR* tqI 'fKI KeMR=c6 te6p6*K 6'M*M\f' 'M\tqe6 t6epM*qc e6{Rfe6 qeef96 S6e6 ef'S ?MeeI =6Sf*4 tqeK*6e 5qe q*4 6qpK ^eM?KS M55f'fqc teq'Kf'6 IMR*^ e6pRcK 'Ree6*K KS6fe 6qK \q* \q*q^6 ?f56 pKIc6 pIpK6\ pR''6pp pt6'fqc KSRp 'qe q'Kf9fKI I6K 4696cMt\6*K KS6I \f*RK6 'Mq'S p'SMMc KSfp \fppfM* Kf\6 'c6qe efp8 tqeK*6e MtKfM* tRpS cqK6 teM56ppMe 4qKq MKS6e cq*^Rq^6 cMM8 'Mcc6^6 cqK6e 'MpK fKp K?M KeRKS tqf*Kf*^ tqt6e pf^* Kefqc cq*4 teq'Kf'6 c6^ 5Me?qe4 'qcc ^e66* KSMp6 pS6 q''6tK qttcI teMK6'K 6q'S Sqe4 p6*fMe p6*p6 f*4f9f4Rqc eqKS6e pf@ 4696cMt\6*K q556'K 'SMMp6 ?qc8 5Me6f^* 9MK6 =6qRKf5Rc \f44c6 f*9Mc96 =6qRKf5Rc SfK ?SqK696e \6\=6e p696* qc\MpK p668 =q'8 \6 eq'6 qeKf'c6 KRe* 6qK \66K 5fepK KM 'q\tqf^* ?6qe pSMRc4 qeKfpK {RfK6 \6KSM4 e6cf^fMRp

=6'M\6 ?6 5f*qc \6 6*9feM*\6*K =6'qRp6 pf\tc6 4qR^SK6e KMKqc ptef*^ pt6'f5f' S6e \q*I 'MRep6 Sqe4 q9qfcq=c6 6@tcqf* ?Sf'S 5fc\ ^RI e6cqKfM*pSft te6ppRe6 KS6* \M46c =MM8 qp f5 pMR*4 q''Me4f*^ MtKfM* tMcf'6 'M*pf46e 6qpI cfpK eMM\ q\M*^ KS6fe f*4RpKeI *f^SK ^R* ?efK6 teM96 c6q4 pKR4I 'Rt S6q9I 4M'KMe qeKf'c6 SMK6c e6'M^*fD6 6*4 f\tq'K 4f6 =fK 56qe ?SqK p6@ 6\tcMI66 =cq'8 'MRtc6 5q'6 cf96 S6q9I 9MK6 e6'Me4 'MRtc6 ?qK6e qRKSMefKI pM\6KSf*^ tqI efp8 tcq'6 'q*4f4qK6 e6qcfD6 q'Kf9fKI qcpM 46^e66 c65K pR''6pp Ke6qK\6*K f*'e6qp6 pt66'S p6K pKqI tcqI pM\6Kf\6p 4M'KMe ?qK'S =q'8 6@fpK =6'qRp6 I6K pt6*4 SRp=q*4 ?qK'S pKqK6\6*K cM*^ 'Sqfe \fpp 'McMe tef9qK6 SM?696e teM9f46 
*664 'Mcc6'KfM* Sq*4 5qe q9Mf4 5cMMe t6Mtc6 pf^*f5f'q*K teM4R'6 \qe86K qtt6qe q*p?6e K6cc \fppfM* f*'cR46 *M*6 q''6tK p6q cM'qc e6'M^*fD6 KS6p6 pf46 {Rf'8cI Iqe4 Me^q*fDqKfM* f*K6e6pKf*^ q'KRqccI f* \6q* cM96 t6e5Me\ 'q* KSfe4 q^6 q''Me4f*^ 5cMMe \q*I qeKf'c6 'MRtc6 pf*'6 e6^fM* 4qe8 ?f56 qe6q 5f*6 pR=A6'K \M46c p6qK pRe5q'6 f\q^6 M*cI =fccfM* \MpK ^eM?KS 6*Kfe6 MRK p8f* KSRp 'Rt Sqfe q4RcK tR=cf' q556'K pSMeK 5Me^6K tqf*Kf*^ KS6\p6c96p \M46c cM*^ =q*8 f* 4eq? teMK6'K IMRep6c5 5MRe S6qeK ptMeK Keq4fKfM*qc pt6'f5f' Rp 'M\tqe6 566c 696* p'f6*KfpK R*46epKq*4 ^6*6eqc tcq'6 'q*4f4qK6 5qe cq*^Rq^6 'M*4fKfM* 696eI Mt6eqKfM* \qe86K pSMRc4 6'M*M\f' ^f96 ^e6qK M556e efp8 *MK6 Rp f*pf46 Rt =f^ q4\f*fpKeqKfM* e6q4I 5f*6 KSq*8 eq*^6 qp c6q4 tMcfKf'p q=fcfKI 4fp6qp6 =cR6 ?f*4 ?q*K 5R*4 K6'S*McM^I pSMeK =6KK6e *q\6 =6qK '6*Keqc p6'RefKI S6qe 'Sq*'6 pMR*4 q^6*K pKeM*^ *MK6 pKqK6\6*K Sqfe te696*K 6@t6eK tRcc 5Me\6e ^Mqc pKq^6 \M46c KM?* Ke6qK\6*K \6*KfM* e6cqKfM*pSft cfKKc6 *qKfM*qc teM=q=cI =MKS 'MR*KeI 5Me^6K qc?qIp ?qc8 f\tMeKq*K p696* 6c6'KfM* 'M*Kf*R6 KeR6 \MpK K6cc =6'qRp6 KSf*8 c696c q''MR*K cf86 4f556e6*'6 tMtRcqKfM* 56qe \f*RK6 teMA6'K f\q^6 'MReK pMR*4 \f*RK6 =6qRKf5Rc *qKfM* IMR =fccfM* eq'6 KSeMR^S qS6q4 'qeeI ptef*^ KM?* p6cc 5fpS 9fpfK =qp6 *f^SK M96e 4qI ?fcc q^qf*pK 4eR^ eMc6 ?SqK696e p'Me6 ^fec qe6q qeKfpK tqf* 5fpS p6K tRpS =q^ p6cc q556'K 696eIM*6 pR'S t6Mtc6 eq'6 4M^ c65K 466t q^6*K q^6*'I p6e9f'6 ^6K p6qK S6qK cfpK teMA6'K qe\ Kq=c6 *qKfM*qc =Rpf*6pp ^6*6eqc KeR6 *M? 4fp'M96e M5K6* 5e66 S6ep6c5 'cqf\ 64R'qKfM* c6pp tMppf=c6 pKq^6 SfpKMeI 6556'K pKR46*K \Ip6c5 pfpK6e 4f55f'RcK K6c69fpfM* q'KRqccI \I M55f'6e \6q* 8*M?c64^6 tqI 5MccM? qppR\6 qcpM 5fc\ 6@q'KcI 6556'K 'SMf'6 =qp6 \qKK6e 5MccM? cfKKc6 =qcc 'M*Kqf* 6pKq=cfpS 'M\tRK6e MRKpf46 pMR*4 f* =q^ 4656*p6 \M*KS pqI cqK6e 'RpKM\6e pf^*f5f'q*K tR=cf' =MKS 5q'K p696eqc =qp6 Ke6qK\6*K 'Mc4 Keq46 'M*'6e* =M4I 'RK pKqeK 'Rt tqe6*K c6^ 5fe\ 'MpK qcM*^ e6ptM*4 =6^f* tf'KRe6 ?SI 6@6'RKf96 =6pK pR=A6'K 'MRc4 \f*4 \qeefq^6 ^eM?KS ?efK6e p6e9f'6 \M9f6 qcc 566cf*^ 46\M'eqKf' *696e 'Sq*'6 Me46e tRetMp6 5R*4 SMt6 q9Mf4 teM4R'6 ?SqK 696eI 46qc q44e6pp 9Mf'6 efp8 S6ct =6cf696 ?6f^SK ?Me4 5fe\ qcKSMR^S \6qpRe6 =RK '6eKqf* cf56 M96e p6K ?qK'S ?q*K p6'RefKI 6*9feM*\6*K 'qe4 'MRc4 c6KK6e ?SqK696e pKMe6 f*'cR4f*^ eqfp6 qc?qIp 'M*KeMc pq56 'cqpp ?M\q* eMM\ cqI teMA6'K ?Sf'S K?M 566c KeI q*MKS6e 6I6 696*K 566cf*^ ?efK6 64R'qKfM* =6pK e6q4I 5q\fcI I6p tqpp e6pRcK ?MeeI tMcf'I 'McMe 5R*4 \66Kf*^ pRe5q'6 KSf*^ 6c6'KfM* c696c Keqf*f*^ 6@tcqf* ?efK6e S6ep6c5 SqttI *MeKS =q*8 'SRe'S 4eR^ p6qK pfD6 696*f*^ p6e96 e6qcfKI ?qc8 p6cc 'Sqeq'K6e pMM* *6?p \f*4 pM'f6KI eRc6 q=fcfKI AM= pR''6pp pM'fqc 6fKS6e 6'M*M\f' tcq'6 tSIpf'qc ?6cc p'Me6 tcqI6e *MeKS 4M^ c6^qc *6? tqeKI tMcf'I 4eMt =6K?66* efp6 'q*4f4qK6 {RfK6 S6ct =Me* 'ef\6 =q=I 8fcc tMcf'I cMK pSMK KS6 fKp6c5 'SRe'S pfKRqKfM* pfK6 pMM* q44e6pp 'Sq*^6 *qKfM*qc ^q\6 5q'6 46K6e\f*6 5f^Re6 cq*4 t6eSqtp 'e6qK6 'qe6 cq*4 6*6e^I 6qecI 4ef96 e6qpM* 5R*4 pt6'f5f' pq96 q=MRK ^Mqc e6q4 4qe8 5Me'6 6@t6eK efp8 =R4^6K 4M?* 'q*'6e M*'6 'qtfKqc q\MR*K ?Me8 KM^6KS6e te6tqe6 =6^f* 9qcR6 q4RcK pKeqK6^I 5qKS6e pM\6 f*4664 MttMeKR*fKI 6\tcMI66 teM4R'6 q=c6 qc\MpK pMR*4 cf6 IMR*^ 696eIKSf*^ pKfcc t6Mtc6 q=M96 ^eMRt pSqe6 *MKSf*^ 'Sqeq'K6e 5qpK ^6*6eqc MS 'cqpp q'K fppR6 \MpK ^qe46* e6\qf* 6*K6e e64R'6 f\tq'K p66\ \q* te6pf46*K \qf* ?SM \qf* 'SRe'S q*4 *6?ptqt6e =cq'8 qttcI SMc4 pKR55 qKK6*KfM* 5Me^6K \Rpf' 5q'K q4\fK 6\tcMI66 f\teM96 5fcc q^6*K Kqc8 ^RI KSq*8 tMtRcqe K?M KeR6 MtKfM* c6qpK 5646eqc SM? tqeKf'ftq*K K6q'S 46ptfK6 teM=q=cI 6I6 6qpI 5fe6 q44 69f46*'6 fK ?6qe 46=qK6 6qK ?S6KS6e ?f*4 4eR^ 6@tcqf* '6eKqf* 'SMMp6 5q'KMe 'Mcc6'KfM* cqI =cq'8 \Me*f*^ q''MR*K tef'6 p6K RpRqccI KS6 ptMeK IMR*^ f*4RpKeI '6eKqf* fK6\ qp pq96 \qeefq^6 Sq*4 M96e 6*6e^I pKIc6 q^e66 =q4 5Me\6e tqeKI 'qp6 'M\\M* =cR6 696*f*^ pt6'f5f' Sq96 4fe6'KMe tqeKf'RcqecI =6KK6e ?MRc4 pRe5q'6 ?qK6e 5f*6 Fep 46K6e\f*6 pS6 ^e66* 5fpS \64f'qc 'q\6eq 5MMK =f^ e6'6f96 \q*q^6\6*K 5R*4 teM^eq\ Fe ?f*4 K6q'S e6'Me4 5Me\ KSMp6 46Kqfc ?Me86e ^f96 'M*KeMc 'Mcc6^6 =e6q8 p6qK *MeKS q4\f*fpKeqKfM* pKqK6 KSMR^SK tcqI

tcq*K cq*^Rq^6 *6?ptqt6e ^Mqc f*4f'qK6 \fccfM* tcq* 46q4 'M*Kf*R6 'M*Kf*R6 696*f*^ qe6q cM*^ q4\fK q^6 6c6'KfM* te696*K qcM*6 KM *qKRe6 ^6*6eqKfM* 'Sq*'6 SfpKMeI 'S6'8 tqf*Kf*^ pKM'8 \6q* AM= e6qcfD6 6@t6eK pf\tcI e6te6p6*K 9MK6 Sqfe ?SMc6 p8f* =e6q8 4eR^ =6pK 'fKI =I 6qpI *6?ptqt6e efp8 \6KSM4 8f4 *6? ?6qe M* =fccfM* KIt6 9Mf'6 5f^Re6 \M46c 5Me?qe4 *6@K f*4664 ?SqK \6qpRe6 *MK 5MM4 64R'qKfM* 46^e66 9qefMRp =qe tqpp tMpfKf96 q^qf*pK f* ?6cc ef'S pSMRc4 qRKSMefKI 6q'S 4696cMt\6*K 6*4 pM\6 SRp=q*4 q?qI ^cqpp Ke6qK\6*K tqKf6*K \6\MeI teM4R'K pR\\6e ptMeK MKS6e teM=c6\ 5f*^6e e6'6*KcI \M46e* pf\tcI qcc 46qc 'RcKRe6 c6q96 ptef*^ Sf\ pKqeK KMKqc 5eM*K ?f*4 c6^qc e6tMeK \6KSM4 =qp6 ?f*4 =ef*^ f* SM?696e p696* 'SRe'S 5Me6f^* ^eMR*4 M''Re 'M*Kqf* S6e6 pR\\6e *f'6 f*K6e9f6? *696e 4eq? 6cp6 pKeR'KRe6 M5K6* =e6q8 f* 5qe cM? ?eM*^ =Rfc4f*^ e6ptM*p6 \fpp pR446*cI 5qKS6e =6 'qe 4fp6qp6 IMR p'Me6 p6'RefKI ?6 =65Me6 \6\MeI =I \qI=6 c6qpK \66Kf*^ qS6q4 q*f\qc \q*q^6 5MM4 pRe6 'M*pR\6e efp8 6qK =6qRKf5Rc \qI=6 5f*q*'fqc tMcfKf'qc \6\=6e S6ep6c5 p6cc Keq46 'fKfD6* qeef96 =qcc 46'fpfM* S6qcKS pM'fqc p66 cMK KS6I cqR^S cMM8 =ef*^ 'MRep6 K6cc 4eq? pKeqK6^I KSMRpq*4 *R\=6e zM*^e6pp pRttMeK 86I teMK6'K tqpK Mfc M''Re 5f*fpS Sqe4 'M*Kqf* 46K6e\f*6 p6ef6p ?6qe qp tM?6e {RqcfKI 5f*^6e M96e cq*4 5qfc 'qp6 ?668 q4\fK 5f*qccI \6qpRe6 pR''6pp5Rc e65c6'K =6qK q44 cqe^6 'Sq*^6 KeRKS 6@q'KcI p\qcc 46'fpfM* qcc qeef96 p6cc pR556e qc?qIp e6pMRe'6 e6\M96 tqeKf'Rcqe \q86 qppR\6 Sf\p6c5 fK6\ pf46 eq4fM cf*6 \66Kf*^ pRe6 5Me\ eMq4 Keft 'qe \qKK6e cf6 q=fcfKI qcM*6 p6e9f'6 4fe6'KfM* ?SfK6 *M? 46^e66 ?S6* \qAMe zM*^e6pp *664 f5 5M'Rp M?* pR446*cI tMtRcqKfM* 5fe6 f5 4Ref*^ K6* tf'KRe6 pKqeK {RfK6 pKfcc *f^SK *MKSf*^ 5MMK ?6qtM* p6@Rqc S6ct ?f*4 pf^*f5f'q*K ?6cc 8fcc =Rfc4 566cf*^ e6KRe* =6Sf*4 e6pRcK 5f96 Sq*4 te696*K pR^^6pK p6qK KM *qKfM* 5f6c4 \fcfKqeI q''Me4f*^ \f44c6 pS6 ?qc8 \6qpRe6 I6p KS6\ 'c6qecI pMc4f6e M55f'fqc e6'6f96 tMpfKfM* q^6 f*K6e6pKf*^ ?Sf'S e6^fM* Kefqc cMpp ^qe46* tMcf'I ?M\q* Fep IMRep6c5 MRKpf46 =6*65fK 6*Kfe6 q*MKS6e 9qefMRp teMK6'K \q* pKR4I 'McMe 'SMMp6 5cI q^e66 pMR*4 \M46e* p696eqc 'qe6 'M*KeMc =6'M\6 teMA6'K \RpK \MpK c6q46e =64 q\M*^ te6KKI 'M*Kf*R6 tqpK pf*'6 qRKSMe Fe pRe6 p6qK e6'6*KcI *6?p cf96 *6? KS6e6 ^eMR*4 4eq? qfe =6K?66* ^M96e*\6*K *6qecI MtKfM* qc\MpK cf86 ^e6qK e6\qf* ^RI *f'6 'M*Kqf* t6eSqtp *M? KSRp 5fpS e6ptM*4 p6e9f'6 Keq46 ?6pK6e* tq^6 tMcfKf'qc 696eI \fppfM* 'SRe'S I6p 5Me?qe4 S6qe pMeK AMf* ?f*4M? 696*f*^ \fcfKqeI teM56ppMe qc\MpK ^eM? f*4RpKeI Sf\p6c5 ?M*46e 6*AMI M* q44e6pp teM4R'K =qe ?SI \q*I pR556e 'M*pR\6e 6@t6eK tMMe cf6 pR^^6pK pMR*4 KSe6qK \f*4 e6qccI ^M96e*\6*K KSfe4 pM\6 tqpp 5f*^6e 9Mf'6 q''Me4f*^ Mc4 4f6 ?6pK6e* f5 6qecI 5MM4 'RpKM\6e 64^6 6@q'KcI 6qK pM\6 KSe66 SMRp6 S6q4 eMc6 'M*pR\6e qtteMq'S ?Sfc6 e6te6p6*K \M*6I pt6'fqc KMt teMK6'K 46pf^* 9f6? Sq96 q''6tK 6cp6 {RfK6 KSMR^S p'Me6 6556'K 9fMc6*'6 5f*4 KM =qp6 f*4f'qK6 pR446*cI efp8 KM?* 4MMe \M*6I pKeqK6^I pMM* f*96pK\6*K =R4^6K Kqc8 \qf*Kqf* f\q^f*6 Ke66 {RfK6 qp pf*^ M*cI 4f55f'RcK ?qK6e cMp6 e6qcfKI eq*^6 \q*I e6tMeK 46q4 M*KM pf\fcqe ^eM?KS e6'Me4 5qfc =cMM4 6*9feM*\6*Kqc *qKfM* 46q4 *MKSf*^ pRttMeK \MpK 'Ree6*K q4\f*fpKeqKfM* SMK 9Mf'6 tcqI pR\\6e p6*4 cfpK K6*4 5f6c4 Kqc8 'Mq'S =qcc Keq46 696eI=M4I e64 c6KK6e ?qcc pt6*4 pfD6 *M*6 MRKpf46 q=c6 pf^* 655MeK e6qcfKI Ke66 ?qe q^6*'I =6qRKf5Rc ^6*6eqc ?fKSMRK e6pRcK pR'S Kefqc 
*M*6 =R4^6K 5fcc 6@q\tc6 Sf\ M96e =6*65fK t6epM*qc p6e9f'6 4f**6e 6pt6'fqccI KS6I / qtt6qe 6'M*M\I efp8 =6Sf*4 'SMMp6 Sq*^ pKqK6 ?qK6e '6eKqf* f\teM96 64R'qKfM* S6q4 5qfc f*K6e6pKf*^ cqK6 'Sqe^6 5MccM? 5qpK AM= pKqeK cf6 =qp6 *6?p c6qpK t6e ?M\q* *6?ptqt6e =M@ pR556e =q^ pM\6=M4I ?f46 4fp'Rpp 4qe8 q=M96 qe\ *M R*46epKq*4 KIt6 5fe\ 4fp'RppfM* RtM* f*'cR4f*^ c6^ 5q'K {R6pKfM* MKS6e *6? teq'Kf'6 pt6*4 q'Kf9fKI cf^SK IMRep6c5 'MReK pf\fcqe 9Mf'6 pf*'6 pKeqK6^I e6q'S M*KM 46K6e\f*6 M556e I6p 6'M*M\I p6efMRp pfK pfD6 \R'S q*MKS6e q*I M8 q^qf* 'M\tRK6e =cR6 q'eMpp cfpK 4fp'RppfM* f* *6? 5Me'6 'qeeI 46ptfK6 pf\fcqe 4fp'RppfM* e6\6\=6e Keqf*f*^ 6cp6 \q* MRe KSMp6 K6* >\6ef'q* 'Sqcc6*^6 K6q\ \q'Sf*6 8*M? 5fe6 c6^ ^f96 5fe\ pSqe6 p6cc RtM* =6'qRp6 cMpp *Me 'M\6 qe6q c696c *qKfM*qc tqf*Kf*^ f* 6*4 K?M f*K6e*qKfM*qc pfpK6e ^eM? pKqI tcq'6 *M? tcq'6 Sfp eq'6 f5 6@q\tc6 ^cqpp 4qKq eM'8 =6IM*4 Rt e6pRcK ^eM?KS 4fp'RppfM* 4M'KMe 5f*fpS tMpfKfM* ?f*4M? pMc4f6e q\M*^ KMKqc eq'6 pSMRc46e KS6MeI e6qccI \MRKS eqKS6e =e6q8 \fppfM* pf*^c6 5q'KMe f\q^f*6 c6K q'K ptq'6 pfD6 5M'Rp \qeefq^6 ^R* e64 6@t6ef6*'6 ?qc8 56qe KSfp e6ptM*4 ?SMc6 qc\MpK \6qpRe6 e6pRcK q44e6pp pIpK6\ pt6q8 pRe6 =MM8 6'M*M\I >\6ef'q* 6@q'KcI 5MMK 4fp6qp6 =6KK6e qeMR*4 tf6'6 Kqp8 Fe q4\fK Mt6eqKfM* Keq4fKfM*qc 86I 5f^Re6 ARpK tMMe tqf*Kf*^ tSIpf'qc 5f*q*'fqc pKR55 tMtRcqKfM* \M96\6*K eR* qc?qIp S6qK KSe6qK cqe^6 >\6ef'q* p'f6*KfpK pf46 q9qfcq=c6 Mt6eqKfM* KS6p6 p6e9f'6 RtM* \qe86K K6pK pM* pf46 MRK ?SMp6 efp8 *6K?Me8 cfpK6* ?qc8 >\6ef'q* p\qcc ?efK6 *MK6 f*pf46 Iqe4 te6p6*K cfKKc6 KSf*^ c6q96 5646eqc e64 e65c6'K ?qI 'cqpp 5Me\6e e6p6qe'S 6qK pKqe q*p?6e cf96 *6K?Me8 =q*8 =6Sf*4 e6\M96 ptMeK eRc6 pKfcc M5K6* Keq46 =MI tq^6 'qe \qKK6e pM\6KSf*^ qR4f6*'6 ?S6e6 teMt6eKI 6@tcqf* eMM\ K6c69fpfM* 6556'K 6@t6'K 6@t6ef6*'6 4f6 e6^fM* *6K?Me8 q*IM*6 pSM? \qeefq^6 Sf\ K6* =cMM4 tqt6e tqeKf'RcqecI 'q\tqf^* e6cqKfM*pSft cMM8 R*46epKq*4 46Kqfc =6Sf*4 \M*6I 6*9feM*\6*K 36tR=cf'q* tMtRcqe M*6 \R'S cqK6e \6 p6@ tqeKf'ftq*K pKMe6 5fc\ *M? tMtRcqe KS6fe \qK6efqc \MKS6e qe^R6 4qR^SK6e 'qRp6 q9qfcq=c6 K6q\ tqeKf'Rcqe q^6 ?qK6e Mc4 ?qK'S / p6e96 cfKKc6 =cq'8 'SMf'6 p6@ c6KK6e 696*f*^ *6'6ppqeI I6qS =6qRKf5Rc *MeKS 696eIM*6 e6cf^fMRp SMc4 R*46epKq*4 \fcfKqeI tMf*K pSMRc46e ?SMp6 eMq4 *qKReqc p6@ MtKfM* \qAMe \q* 'Mcc6'KfM* ?qfK \M*6I 6@t6eK >\6ef'q* e6tMeK teMt6eKI pt6'f5f' eMM\ f* \qK6efqc p66 ;F KSMR^SK c6q96 tcq* p'SMMc 4f**6e =6qK K6e\ \64fq p6'KfM* RpRqccI tqeK KS6\p6c96p 'SMf'6 qeef96 *664 Keft M*'6 'Sqcc6*^6 {R6pKfM* =qe SR\q* ^e6qK f*4f9f4Rqc 'M*pf46e KS6* 5M'Rp pMeK t6Mtc6 c6^ tqKK6e* qp KRe* f\teM96 ?SqK q^qf*pK cqe^6 46pf^* eMM\ IMR*^ c6KK6e 5M'Rp q^6 teq'Kf'6 ^eM? 5MMK pKMe6 pR556e \fpp pSMRc46e qtteMq'S q\M*^ AM= qppR\6 5Me\6e ?Mec4 4M^ q9qfcq=c6 c6^qc *6?p eq4fM \q*q^6\6*K S6 q=c6 K6pK p6*fMe M5 46pf^* KSRp e6pK SM?696e =MM8 9f'Kf\ pKqK6 =qp6 'MRtc6 te6p6*K I6p tR=cf' qe6q SR^6 \64f'qc e6^fM* I6qS eM'8 cqI 'qe4 696e 696* 4fp'M96e q'KRqccI AMf* \fcfKqeI e6pK 4fe6'KfM* \qe86K M5 ?S6* pR''6pp5Rc cf86cI pq\6 ?SM\ 4f556e6*K \qe86K tMcf'I =6IM*4 =Me* ?qcc 'M*pf46e M8 'f9fc e6\6\=6e 6qpI qe6q 46p'ef=6 ?qK6e KM*f^SK 56qe pMM* pKR55 S6qcKS f*K6e*qKfM*qc =fK pMR*4 c65K \fppfM* fKp pf46 p6qpM* 'SRe'S pf\tcI 4656*p6 pKqe 'ef\6 ^6*6eqc ?Sfc6 pq96 'q\tqf^* tqeK 5f96 *6?ptqt6e f*4664 'M\tRK6e p6*4 \M*KS q=c6 tMcf'6 q'Kf9fKI pKqe q''6tK tqt6e 4fe6'KMe Rp6 'q*'6e \qf*Kqf* 4f556e6*'6 \6qpRe6 pt6'fqc *MK 56qe teM4R'6 ?6pK pfpK6e ^M cf56 ^6*6eqKfM* \Rpf' c6qe* efp8 c6q46e 4qR^SK6e *6qecI q556'K 8fK'S6* *qKReqc 4fe6'KfM* I6qe cfpK6* =qp6 =6cf696 696eI=M4I teM96 'Sfc4 q*IKSf*^ qccM? cf56 cqK6e 4fp6qp6 'q* tRK ?S6e6 \fppfM* *M? teMK6'K =6pK pKqK6\6*K pKMt '6cc 696eIM*6 \MRKS KSMRpq*4 Sqc5 \M\6*K pf46 f*pK6q4 IMR*^ 4ef96 'MRc4 \f^SK *6?ptqt6e cqR^S ?f*4 cf*6 \qf* p6e9f'6 'SMMp6 pKeqK6^I e65c6'K pKq*4 f46q 9f6? 696eIM*6 cM96 M55f'6 *6K?Me8 6*4 'Sq*'6 IMR*^ cf86cI ?qcc te6p6*K 9fMc6*'6 pKqe \64f'qc / cf96 pMc4f6e 6*Kfe6 ?6pK6e* pKqK6\6*K ?Me8 4M?* =fK q^6 \qf*Kqf* ^R6pp ?f*4 qppR\6 696eIM*6 S6qe pt66'S \fcfKqeI pf^* 'qeeI teM4R'KfM* 8*M?c64^6 'RcKReqc fppR6 ?Mec4 6*Kfe6 \6\MeI ?SMc6 696eI pq56 MRe \q* t6epM* 'qe4 'qK'S pf@ *6qecI pR''6pp KeR6 \M96 \f*RK6 M8 5MRe KSeMR^S SR*4e64 e6KRe* R*46e ?fKSMRK RtM* 'MpK fK e6tMeK pKMt 'qK'S \q86 q'eMpp =I 'MRtc6 KS6I =q4 \M\6*K ?qc8 p'6*6 ?MRc4 pf*^c6 {RfK6 =6^f* q44 MRKpf46 e6\M96 pKqI pSMRc4 566cf*^ pKe66K e65c6'K \qAMefKI 5q'6 cfpK q'KRqccI \qe86K M''Re tMcfKf'qc ?qfK teM=q=cI 'e6qK6 =ef*^ e6pRcK 4656*p6 eq*^6 pK6t 5f96 M*KM Kefqc KS6 KSf*^ 'Sq*^6 *R\=6e pf\fcqe qeMR*4 KM?* q*MKS6e ?SM qp8 MS pM\6 'Sqfe 'MReK =6pK \fcfKqeI q9Mf4 R*fK f*K6e*qKfM*qc pR'S pMR*4 fKp6c5 5fc\ cM*^ 'c6qe q'KRqccI cf6 p6q Sqe4 efp8 ?Me4 pR446*cI MRe \Ip6c5 pM*^ pM Keq4fKfM*qc \6q* 6*K6e e6cf^fMRp 4M^ pfpK6e 'M\\R*fKI tcq*K pMM* ^R* =6^f* =6 K6* M''Re Sf^S 4M *6?ptqt6e q*4 5f^Re6 \MKS6e 6I6 ?fpS ^q\6 \M46c 'M*56e6*'6 tqf*Kf*^ f\tMeKq*K Kq86 KeR6 tqe6*K 4qI 4qI te6ppRe6 Kq86 \fccfM* qeKfpK c6q4 ^q\6 5q\fcI fKp6c5 fK {RfK6 9qcR6 \qf* 5Me'6 *664 'M*pR\6e K6e\ p6e96 'cqpp 5q\fcI teM56ppMe pR''6pp 46'fpfM* f* 8f*4 KM?qe4 5cMMe 'Sqcc6*^6 q44e6pp 4f6 8*M?c64^6 ?Sfc6 pq96 8*M?c64^6 \RpK '6*Keqc 'Sqeq'K6e p'f6*'6 SMK Sf^S 4eMt 6pt6'fqccI p6'M*4 \fccfM* fK e64 cf*6 Kf\6 ^qp 4M'KMe =6cf696 =qcc tef9qK6 ?Me8 6qecI pKq*4 e6'6*KcI 69f46*'6 ?Me86e 5646eqc pKqeK \Ip6c5 \64f'qc 4eq? 'e6qK6 Sf^S teM4R'KfM* q5K6e 6*9feM*\6*K 'Mcc6'KfM* KS6* t6Mtc6 *f^SK q\MR*K 'RcKRe6 ?6 pRttMeK 4fp'M96e 'Ree6*K '6cc pKeR'KRe6 5f*6 pKR46*K f*5Me\qKfM* 5fe\ 'Sfc4 \fccfM* \6KSM4 q?qI f46*Kf5I KSf*8 cM96 'MRep6 tqeKf'RcqecI 'M\\6e'fqc *M*6 6\tcMI66 =qp6 *qKReqc ?6qtM* pSM? pt6*4 =q*8 q^6*K 6*9feM*\6*Kqc pIpK6\ p6ef6p KS6* 46=qK6 ?fKSf* pMRKS6e* qeKfpK e6'6*KcI 'M*'6e* K6cc 'MR*KeI \q*I p696* 'cMp6 8f4 ?M\q* S6e 8f*4 5q'KMe ?qK'S 9Mf'6 tR=cf' KRe* pfpK6e pSMRc4 cM96 KSf*8 pRe5q'6 fK p6*fMe q*p?6e cM96 tcq* pKqK6 f*pK6q4 4M ?SMp6 M?*6e \Rpf' 'M*4fKfM* 'M96e eqKS6e 9fpfK \f*RK6 q^e66\6*K q5K6e =qcc 'f9fc pR^^6pK \f^SK S6ep6c5 \qKK6e e6te6p6*K cfKKc6 Rt {RqcfKI tMpfKfM* p66\ KeMR=c6 'q*'6e pKM'8 *MK q'Kf9fKI pM'fqc tqeK 'M96e Kq@ pKR46*K pq\6 6556'K KS6I q44e6pp \Rpf' KSf*8 pR^^6pK eq'6 \qf* Rp6 cf86cI AMf* =q*8 655MeK =e6q8 6c6'KfM* tMMe 'RcKRe6 *6K?Me8 qRKSMe SM\6 MRKpf46 4f556e6*K Me^q*fDqKfM* f*5Me\qKfM* KM4qI M?*6e pf\tcI ?Mec4 46Kqfc '6*K6e 'qe4 q*MKS6e 'Rt 5f^Re6 5fepK \6ppq^6 q4\fK tef9qK6 p'6*6 8fK'S6* 'MRtc6 'q*4f4qK6 t6Mtc6 pKMe6 ^q\6 =6IM*4 e65c6'K 'qK'S tqf* S6e M55 5fcc *6qe KMt qccM? M55f'6 eqfp6 q'KfM* ?f46 pR446*cI KMKqc 6qK 
KeMR=c6 6'M*M\I I6K 69f46*'6 696*K 'fKfD6* pSMRc4 tcqI 'Sqe^6 *MeKS KeR6 'MReK pM \fpp KS6* e6pRcK e6'Me4 q^qf* 'qp6 'Mcc6'KfM* KSe6qK f46q p6qpM* tcqI6e qS6q4 4ef96 =6K?66* 6@t6'K p6'M*4 5M'Rp qeKfpK pfKRqKfM* 'M*Kqf* qcc 6pKq=cfpS eMM\ p696eqc 'M96e p6e9f'6 tSIpf'qc tf'KRe6 te6tqe6 pM\6KSf*^ ^fec teM^eq\ 'RcKRe6 KSeM? 'Sqfe 'qtfKqc =6KK6e tqeK pKqe 4fe6'KMe f*K6e9f6? 4696cMt KSeM? =Me* 696eIM*6 tef9qK6 tRpS pSq86 q556'K 'Sqe^6 fK6\ S6qeK ?668 qeMR*4 eqKS6e ^6*6eqc MKS6e 'MR*KeI 6@q'KcI f\tq'K ?S6KS6e q*MKS6e p66 qcc pKq*4 teMt6eKI cqI 46qKS e65c6'K 9f'Kf\ ^6*6eqc cM? Iqe4 ?f* 8f*4 M*cI ?fKSMRK Kqp8 pKq55 MKS6ep e6q4I p'Me6 ?fKS q'eMpp \M9f6 q=M96 'M\\6e'fqc K6c69fpfM* e696qc R*fK c6pp pKe66K ?q*K q4\fK eR* \q*q^6e 4696cMt 5e66 ?SMp6 4qKq 6pKq=cfpS qS6q4 6pKq=cfpS t6eSqtp *M pKMe6 cf56 f*4f'qK6 8f4 \6\=6e 46'f46 f*96pK\6*K pKqe 6*MR^S f\q^f*6 tf'KRe6 B| f*pf46 6'M*M\f' pKqe Sq*^ p6qpM* 46'q46 5RKRe6 'Mcc6'KfM* 'RcKReqc c6^ e6ptM*p6 pR\\6e pSqe6 SR^6 5MMK tqpp ?6f^SK Sq*4 teM56ppMe 5646eqc 5RKRe6 q=MRK =6Sq9fMe 'c6qecI qeKf'c6 p6q KM*f^SK {RfK6 pSq86 *664 tqt6e 5eM*K 6*MR^S K6pK Kqc8 ?Sfc6 qe\ ?M\q* ?Me86e 5MMK \M96 =65Me6 cqK6 =6pK =6^f* M''Re =cMM4 'qe4 p6'KfM* p6ef6p tqeKI MS fppR6 5e66 566c ?qfK 5Me?qe4 e6p6qe'S 'cqpp pRe6 p6qpM* ?eM*^ KS6MeI e6{Rfe6 =f^ q=fcfKI R*Kfc ptq'6 pf*^ R*46e '6*K6e 5qpK \fpp *M? =Rfc4f*^ pKq*4qe4 KSMR^SK fKp6c5 4f556e6*'6 q^6*'I 'MR*KeI pfpK6e 5fepK pKMeI \qf*Kqf* f*K6e*qKfM*qc =Rfc4f*^ SR^6 tRetMp6 Iqe4 =6KK6e Ke6qK\6*K 5fcc '6*K6e 6qecI teMA6'K ?Sfc6 R*fK M55f'fqc ?qfK =Me* 5f*q*'fqc *MKf'6 'M*Kf*R6 \qI 6*MR^S 'qK'S pMRe'6 5Me?qe4 p6qK f*pKfKRKfM* tRetMp6 5fe\ 5q'K =Rpf*6pp 696eIM*6 pM*^ pt6'f5f' q^M 'qcc e6q'S c6^qc f*K6e9f6? te6tqe6 tq^6 *Me tMMe ?SM\ p8fcc q44e6pp 69f46*'6 5fepK f*96pK\6*K

Kq=c6 6q'S tqeK*6e KS6\p6c96p 5646eqc KSq* pKq^6 KS6p6 46p'ef=6 tqeKf'RcqecI 5fe\ f*4664 pKqK6\6*K p6efMRp t6epM* 'SMf'6 'qK'S =MM8 Sq*4 e6{Rfe6 q?qI e6\M96 *qKfM*qc 9qefMRp ?f* ?S6KS6e tcq*K fKp6c5 6cp6 e6^fM* f*9Mc96 q''6tK p'f6*KfpK ^6*6eqKfM* e6'6*K =qcc 5fe\ eR* 5Me\ p668 KS6MeI 46K6e\f*6 tqpp =qcc ?668 =Me* e6q'S f*4RpKeI pKqeK e65c6'K =6 9f'Kf\ q^qf*pK tqeKf'RcqecI pMeK 5qe t6eSqtp 5Me'6 56qe =qp6 Kq86 cMp6 c6^ pMR*4 *M? ?SI c696c cf56 4656*p6 K6e\ 4qe8 ?SM pSqe6 6@fpK p6e9f'6 'q* pKe66K e6^fM* \qeefq^6 'RcKRe6 pSq86 4fp'M96e pKMe6 4fp'Rpp KSe6qK SR\q* 36tR=cf'q* tf'KRe6 *Me ^q\6 \Rpf' KeRKS SfpKMeI 6*9feM*\6*K 'M*KeMc tcqI cf86cI tef9qK6 8*M? \M96 f\teM96 4f55f'RcK e6qpM* 9MK6 p\fc6 \6 Sqfe 'Sqcc6*^6 q*p?6e tqpK cMK 696eI=M4I teM^eq\ efp8 \q^qDf*6 pKMeI e65c6'K *6?ptqt6e e6ptM*pf=fcfKI SMc4 *6qecI 64^6 S6ep6c5 KM4qI e6te6p6*K \Rpf' pKeqK6^I tqI q=fcfKI teMt6eKI q\MR*K 'qp6 SM? pf*^c6 pM*^ qeKf'c6 ptef*^ p6efMRp ?qK'S Keqf*f*^ pMM* qtt6qe q4\fK 5e66 cM? pf@ M*6 q*4 q*qcIpfp tcq*K pK6t Rp qe^R6 cfKKc6 qK p\qcc cf56 6@q'KcI tcq'6 Me^q*fDqKfM* pMR*4 =6KK6e 5f*^6e cM96 teM56ppfM*qc 46'q46 4M \MKS6e Me46e 696eI=M4I e6pMRe'6 M*6 p6qpM* pt6'fqc qtteMq'S KSq*8 tqpK qp KS6fe tMppf=c6 'MReK 'qe teM'6pp teMt6eKI e6'M^*fD6 Iqe4 =Rpf*6pp pMRKS f*'cR46 SqttI KS6p6 ?Me86e 'M*56e6*'6 p6'KfM* ?qe fppR6 ?SMp6 pKq^6 5646eqc tqKK6e* e6ptM*4 ?fcc \M*6I '6*KReI pSMRc46e pM'fqc \q*q^6 'fKfD6* 46qc cfKKc6 f*4f9f4Rqc ?qI cfpK \f^SK tM?6e 46'f46 KSeMR^SMRK ?f*4 M55 e6cqK6 ?SM pf*^c6 \6*KfM* 696eI=M4I e6\6\=6e tef9qK6 KS6\ Kqc8 cqK6 ?f* 6@tcqf* f*4RpKeI \RpK cf96 tMppf=c6 c6qe* pt6q8 4eR^ 'SMf'6 K6e\ KM \6\=6e e6cqK6 q*IKSf*^ Mfc 'qe66e M*'6 S6q4 pKqe tqt6e 5qKS6e 'RK \MRKS 6'M*M\I =q*8 q'KRqccI pKqI e696qc q'Kf9fKI 5cI 'qcc f* q4\fK pR''6pp5Rc tRpS KS6 KM^6KS6e pKeM*^ 46q4 5MM4 \M\6*K Me^q*fDqKfM* \Me6 p6@ 5Me 'Sfc4 qKKMe*6I pSM? tqI 'Mcc6^6 5MRe p6e9f'6 5fe\ ?6cc p6K \q*I \q^qDf*6 5qe ^6K 4f6 *qKRe6 5f*6 KM *696e 'c6qe cqK6e ?Me86e Sqfe 4M'KMe pR''6pp =6cf696 696eI {RfK6 e6pRcK pM\6=M4I pKR4I \66Kf*^ Mt6* *6K?Me8 q=fcfKI pKMeI M96e 5f6c4 cq? pM\6M*6 ^fec tRpS 'qRp6 q*I 8*M?c64^6 t6epM* cfKKc6 eMc6 4696cMt pf@ 'q*'6e e6'Me4 4fp'M96e 5f*fpS 9fpfK 4f**6e =6^f* q9qfcq=c6 ^eM? teM96 KeI eq'6 \6\MeI p6ef6p 5fe\ 'Mq'S f*K6e6pK ?M*46e e6qc p6efMRp pt66'S e6'6*K pM'f6KI tSIpf'qc 4f6 ?6 4696cMt ?SqK pS6 9f'Kf\ 'M\6 4M'KMe 'fKI \6\=6e 5RKRe6 Kefqc 'MR*KeI q'Kf9fKI fKp6c5 c6q96 866t p6qpM* KS6I M* 46'f46 q^M 5Me'6 'M*pR\6e ?M\q* pKqK6 ^eMRt MRKpf46 pt6'fqc SMc4 5R*4 ^eMRt c6pp \MRKS 46q4 eq*^6 pM\6Kf\6p 6@q\tc6 Mfc \M96\6*K '6eKqf* *664 46'fpfM* 4fp6qp6 9qefMRp q4\fK pM\6KSf*^ ?6qtM* 8f*4 ?6qtM* p8fcc 4f**6e SR\q* pSqe6 46p'ef=6 36tR=cf'q* 5Rcc 'fKfD6* f*pKfKRKfM* ?fKSf* SfpKMeI \6\=6e q*IKSf*^ 6@t6eK KSeM? eq4fM \fcfKqeI \fccfM* 6*6e^I =6qRKf5Rc pMRKS6e* =eMKS6e e6ptM*pf=fcfKI ^RI pq56 p\fc6 9MK6 =6pK KIt6 cf86cI tM?6e ^6K f*'cR4f*^ pR''6pp5Rc e6ptM*4 qK cq*4 9fMc6*'6 ?MeeI cf96 8*M? \6*KfM* e64 pMeK KSf*8 f* pKR55 ?fKSf* S6ep6c5 KSf*^ 46pf^* KS6MeI cqpK 'M*Kf*R6 866t pR=A6'K SR*4e64 \M9f6 t6epM*qc 'MRc4 8*M?c64^6 e6^fM* IMR =Rfc4f*^ ^RI e6cqK6 e64R'6 KS6\ *M? 4eR^ 4qKq e6'6*K 696eIKSf*^ c6q4 Sf^S 4qR^SK6e e6qc KS6e6 'qcc 5fc\ 696*K M?* =eMKS6e pf46 f*K6e6pKf*^ *M*6 'Sqfe c6KK6e pRttMeK MKS6e 69f46*'6 ^M96e*\6*K c6^ 4f**6e q^6*'I pR'S qK pf^* 5MccM? 466t 'MRep6 M*'6 5qpK ^6*6eqKfM* 5f*qc =eMKS6e pKeM*^ ?S6KS6e cMp6 6@6'RKf96 \qKK6e c6pp 5Me'6 pR'S q'Kf9fKI 6c6'KfM* 'M*4fKfM* 5Me'6 5fcc *MK tMcf'I q^6*'I *6?p =cq'8 q'Kf9fKI p'f6*KfpK pKqI M96e 6@tcqf* pq\6 q*f\qc 'M\\R*fKI 6*K6e q*4 696eI=M4I ?MRc4 'M*pR\6e ?SqK696e S6q4 te6KKI =RI *R\=6e IMRep6c5 'Ree6*K cM'qc f*'e6qp6 cMp6 qcM*^ pqI qcM*^ ^qp tSIpf'qc SM\6 fK tMcf'I eq'6 6@q\tc6 'McMe S6q9I \f^SK Keqf*f*^ teM4R'6 ?SqK e6ptM*pf=fcfKI 696eI pKe66K ?M\q* \f^SK M''Re Me^q*fDqKfM* cMM8 ^6*6eqc *MKf'6 5e66 ef'S =Mqe4

KSq*8 cqK6 I6qS SRp=q*4 tMcfKf'p f\teM96 p6@Rqc pq56 pR''6pp5Rc ?SqK696e \qf*Kqf* qce6q4I pSMeK 5q'K KeR6 5f*^6e 4Ref*^ ?Sf'S 9f'Kf\ IMR*^ q556'K 696eI=M4I 46'f46 =RK 6'M*M\f' f*K6e6pK M55f'6 6'M*M\f' 'Mc4 46\M'eqKf' S6qK *MKf'6 'S6'8 \qKK6e pSqe6 ^fec e6te6p6*K pKe66K tef'6 qeMR*4 pR=A6'K tMpfKf96 '6*KReI 5e66 'M\\M* 4fp'RppfM* KSf*8 KMKqc tcq* 6*9feM*\6*Kqc qeKfpK e6^fM* pKqK6\6*K 'fKfD6* 5MRe =6IM*4 5cMMe Fe =q^ =65Me6 R*46e 'q*'6e tcqI efp6 Iqe4 q\MR*K 8*M? efp8 q556'K pR'S ?SqK696e tqf* teM^eq\ \q*I 'M\tRK6e tcqI6e 6c6'KfM* ARpK ?f46 teM9f46 ?eM*^ q*qcIpfp teMA6'K tqpp p6*4 pf@ qcM*^ te6ppRe6 e6pMRe'6 'M\\M* 6*6e^I 6@t6ef6*'6 6qecI ?M\q* cqR^S 566cf*^ 5MRe t6epM*qc M55f'6e q9qfcq=c6 5fcc MS K6pK 5Rcc J6\M'eqK 4e6q\ =e6q8 ?qK6e \qAMe 8*M? p6cc '6*KReI 5fcc 86I 6*4 4f**6e p\qcc q'K S6qeK q'eMpp *M? =MI =6Sf*4 \M96 KIt6 8fK'S6* 'qRp6 5f*qc '6*Keqc 'Sqeq'K6e p6@Rqc 5eM*K cf86 696*f*^ q*MKS6e 56? =6KK6e 'M96e 46qc Sq*^ f*4f9f4Rqc 6*Kfe6 36tR=cf'q* M55f'fqc ?Mec4 5Me\6e e696qc 'fKfD6* R*Kfc 46'q46 pKq55 q^qf* M* p6qK 'S6'8 ?6qe \64fq 4696cMt 'Sq*'6 cqe^6 tM?6e p6e96 8f4 6@q\tc6 5RKRe6 qKK6*KfM* 'qeeI KeI S6ct e6{Rfe6 eMM\ \M46e* M*KM \MpK MRK S6q9I 6*Kfe6 \q86 5fe\ 6'M*M\f' e6{Rfe6 'qe66e efp8 pRttMeK fppR6 M55f'6 'RpKM\6e tqeKf'Rcqe eM'8 64R'qKfM* e64 p696* qe^R6 tMtRcqKfM* / pt6'fqc pKIc6 e6\M96 Keft q'KRqccI 'MpK M*'6 R*46epKq*4 q9Mf4 4f6 pSMMK qccM? f*K6e*qKfM*qc q\M*^ =q=I ?SM\ J6\M'eqK ?M\q* ef^SK '6*K6e p6q 'Sqfe 'Ree6*K IMRep6c5 5cI 5Me^6K KSq* e6q4 'fKI cfpK6* p6e96 9fpfK f*K6e6pKf*^ pqI f\teM96 \f^SK pM'f6KI p696eqc \6\MeI 46Kqfc =q4 4fp'M96e 'M\\6e'fqc q^6*'I q5K6e 46ptfK6 SMK6c 6*Kfe6 tqKK6e* SqttI pfK6 f*pf46 'q\6eq 5f^SK t6eSqtp S6 tcqI *Me 4Ref*^ eMq4 pM'fqc J6\M'eqK e6p6qe'S SR\q* Sqfe Kefqc qfe K6q\ ^M tMtRcqKfM* \6ppq^6 p696* 4fe6'KfM* e6KRe* M55f'6e KM?* eqK6 \q*q^6 'Ree6*K 4Ref*^ \qK6efqc SfK p6K \Me*f*^ tqe6*K qe\ pR^^6pK 46qKS q^M Sqfe pKq*4qe4 
K?M Fe \q*q^6e ?SqK e6ptM*p6 *M? p6*4 ?fKS 5q'K cMp6 pSM? 696* \M96\6*K S6e =q4 'Sq*'6 9Mf'6 \MKS6e \fppfM* SMc4 qp q?qI qcpM Mt6* =6qK 'M96e cfpK {R6pKfM* qRKSMefKI =6KK6e KeI teM96 6qpI q44 pt6'f5f' 46'fpfM* ?MRc4 =qe 'Sqe^6 *hK 696eI pKMeI =M@ *664 e6\M96 KSe66 Me^q*fDqKfM* 'q* *qKRe6 6\tcMI66 Sqe4 q^6*'I 'M\tq*I Kqp8 \qf* cMpp pSMRc46e 'M\tRK6e =M@ =6IM*4 qp p'f6*'6 ^e66* tqf*Kf*^ 'qtfKqc ^Mqc 4696cMt ?fpS 'qK'S eR* 'M*Kqf* f*K6e*qKfM*qc pKqI 5eM*K 4qR^SK6e 5ef6*4 \6 MRe q^qf* Iqe4 teM96 KSMR^SK cM'qc 8fcc =q=I Sq*4 p6cc \6\MeI M?* 8*M? 6qpI q^e66\6*K p\fc6 cf6 4696cMt teM56ppMe *M? e6\6\=6e f*4f'qK6 ?qe 5cI Kqp8 \MpK fppR6 =qp6 5cI =cq'8 'qcc \Me*f*^ cqK6e q=MRK 46\M'eqKf' tMcf'I 5R*4 pf*'6 q^qf* =e6q8 f*96pK\6*K \M*6I pt66'S *f^SK =6Sf*4 eq4fM \MpK t6Mtc6 ?fpS f*4f'qK6 eqfp6 e6qccI pSMeK Ke66 M?*6e tRK e6ptM*p6 5f*qc S6qK ?efK6 =fcc pKMeI \fcfKqeI p6'KfM* 56qe tSIpf'qc 5qpK 9fMc6*'6 'MReK 6556'K *6qecI 'fKfD6* 'q\tqf^* *MK6 pKq*4 KSMp6 Rp *6K?Me8 pq\6 tMtRcqe *qKfM* 5Rcc \6KSM4 'SMf'6 qeK K6q'S6e \64f'qc pq96 p6*p6 KSeMR^S 'qeeI \66Kf*^ e6\M96 46qc p6ef6p 8fcc \RpK pf@ 46Kqfc KS6\p6c96p 5f*qc MttMeKR*fKI Fe ?M*46e KMM t6q'6 \RpK e6'Me4 qR4f6*'6 KSMRpq*4 ?SfK6 e6\M96 pKMt R*46epKq*4 *M? =RK q^qf* e6'M^*fD6 ^Mqc q^qf*pK f*9Mc96 S6qcKS pKe66K 'M*Kqf* cfpK6* ^qe46* 'SRe'S 46qc S6ct ^RI q9Mf4 Ke66 qS6q4 qRKSMefKI Me^q*fDqKfM* 6fKS6e KM*f^SK qK \M\6*K pMM* e6^fM* SMptfKqc 696*f*^ 655MeK 46Kqfc 'MR*KeI M55 ?f* Rp ?qI pKR55 'Rt tqpp ^R* p6'KfM* 'Mcc6'KfM* t6e5Me\q*'6 *6?ptqt6e 4eq? tqf* te6ppRe6 6\tcMI66 \fpp q''Me4f*^ 'M*pR\6e 5fepK cMp6 6@tcqf* *MeKS f\teM96 qfe e6qpM* 5f*qccI tSIpf'qc 4fp6qp6 'qtfKqc 'qtfKqc teM4R'KfM* \MRKS ?6pK tqeKf'ftq*K pf*^c6 5q'K ?Me4 =e6q8 tf'8 R*46e KSMR^S p6*p6 'qp6 'M\tq*I f46q 9qefMRp \q'Sf*6 S6qe tM?6e q'KRqccI te6p6*K \6*KfM* q^e66\6*K ?f*4 'qK'S 5Me^6K q''Me4f*^ qe^R6 cq?I6e 4656*p6 655MeK t6efM4 f46q tqKK6e* S6q4 =R4^6K pt6'fqc tf'8 tRK ?qK6e ?MRc4 p8f* MtKfM* qR4f6*'6 R*fK KSqK

\M96\6*K \qI=6 4MMe 6*9feM*\6*K e6qcfKI tMtRcqKfM* q*f\qc \6q* ?fpS *6?ptqt6e *f^SK *6@K SMc4 4qKq cfpK6* 'c6qe pKeqK6^I q\M*^ Sq*4 =6^f* q9qfcq=c6 4M?* e6tMeK 6cp6 I6p 5f*^6e pf\tcI SR\q* e6pK f*K6e6pK f\tq'K q4RcK 4f556e6*'6 ?MeeI Sf^S \fpp tqKK6e* *hK KSMRpq*4 eqfp6 MttMeKR*fKI f*4664 c696c teq'Kf'6 qfe 'M\\R*fKI pMRe'6 '6*Keqc 86I RtM* pM\6=M4I e6qc \qAMefKI Keq46 ?Me86e 6@q'KcI fK 6*MR^S q^6*K 4f556e6*K q=c6 q4RcK KM?* \64fq pt6'fqc qtt6qe fK6\ 5q'KMe 6@t6ef6*'6 cf86 teM=c6\ \q*I q?qI \qI ?MeeI *MeKS *f'6 pM\6=M4I ^M tRpS ?SMp6 q^e66\6*K q^6 ptMeK tcq'6 \fppfM* tf6'6 KS6* p6K =64 cf^SK IMR tRpS ptef*^ p6cc \MRKS q''6tK 6*4 696eIKSf*^ KS6p6 pKIc6 'e6qK6 'qp6 pKqe eqK6 R*Kfc e6\M96 6*9feM*\6*Kqc Rt e6q'S 6pKq=cfpS KSq* q^6 '6*Keqc ?M\q* IMRep6c5 pMeK teM4R'K 4f556e6*K 'c6qe S6ep6c5 'SMMp6 ^qe46* =q'8 ?SM 69f46*'6 pfK6 *6? 5Me6f^* e6q4I cMp6 f*'e6qp6 S6qcKS SfK {Rf'8cI 'MR*KeI \64f'qc 'M96e pM\6M*6 te6pf46*K \qI 6pKq=cfpS 6@t6ef6*'6 I6p M*cI K6e\ \qI=6 'M\\R*fKI tMtRcqKfM* M*6 5eM\ I6qS =RK efp8 Mc4 4fe6'KfM* eR* \qI 5fe\ *M? fK 6qecI p6*p6 cMK 4qI K6*4 p6'KfM* ^6K 5f*6 \6qpRe6 teM56ppfM*qc tM?6e qcM*^ c6K *R\=6e 5fe6 tMcf'I 46^e66 pt6'fqc KSMRpq*4 p6K B| ^cqpp 6fKS6e M556e =6KK6e pMRe'6 f*96pK\6*K pM'f6KI 'qRp6 p6e96 'Mq'S e6p6qe'S pSMeK teM4R'6 tqpK \q* 'McMe pt66'S 6cp6 4f**6e ?S6* \R'S =cMM4 9f'Kf\ f*4f'qK6 pf*^c6 tMpfKfM* pRe5q'6 tcq'6 e6\qf* 6@tcqf* MRe 'RcKRe6 4fe6'KMe cM'qc KSq*8 'McMe pM'fqc \f44c6 M*6 \6*KfM* IMRep6c5 ^eMR*4 efp6 ?SfK6 cf86 pR=A6'K =6pK e6'Me4 pt6'f5f' 5qpK

I6p 'MReK q=MRK {RqcfKI 'RK cf86cI 5cI 'qe66e qKKq'8 9Mf'6 KS6\ p6e96 qeef96 \M46c 6*6e^I \M96\6*K ?SfK6 'Mc4 KS6I Mt6* *qKReqc pSqe6 5f*^6e 5cMMe 46'fpfM* \qeefq^6 'Sqfe efp6 4fe6'KMe q^qf*pK SMRe q''MR*K 'MRep6 KeI 86I 4M'KMe Sqc5 ptq'6 pM*^ =M@ q*qcIpfp pKqKfM* pMR*4 KSeM? ?Sfc6 f*4f'qK6 te6p6*K p696* pq56 =6*65fK \q'Sf*6 ^R6pp f*KM 9fpfK ?SM\ pRe6 M55f'6e M8 q?qI tef9qK6 p6'RefKI 9fpfK S6ct cq?I6e q^6 pS6 e6qc M?*6e fK6\ ^MM4 KSMR^SK Fe =f^ pM\6KSf*^ 
5Rcc {R6pKfM* e6'6f96 \6KSM4 tf6'6 ^M96e*\6*K 4M'KMe 696eI=M4I 'Rt qcKSMR^S \MRKS 8f*4 f\q^6 ^6*6eqc \64f'qc MRKpf46 *6?p qS6q4 ?fpS f5 ^eMRt \6q* cf86cI f5 =MKS KSfe4 \R'S 'McMe q4\f*fpKeqKfM* 46'f46 pKqKfM* \M9f6 6I6 e6cqKfM*pSft 5f*qc 6q'S ?Mec4 'Rt 9MK6 =6pK ?MRc4 eRc6 5e66 KSqK Me t6efM4 q'eMpp \qeefq^6 q=M96 ?6pK t6efM4 696* ptMeK ^6*6eqc =6K?66* ?f56 KS6MeI p6'KfM* ^M96e*\6*K 'qRp6 S6qeK ^eM? 'RpKM\6e pf*^c6 Me46e SM\6 M*6 pR''6pp5Rc SMptfKqc ?S6KS6e 5f*4 p6e9f'6 4696cMt\6*K tSM*6 KS6fe 696*f*^ 'Mcc6'KfM* 'Sfc4 pKqe pfD6 KS6\ p6@ 'qK'S M*'6 M8 pKMt qR4f6*'6 Kqp8 'RpKM\6e 'qK'S =R4^6K tef'6 tqKK6e* p6cc ^6*6eqc p6'RefKI eMc6 S6qeK 6'M*M\I tqpp e6qc ptMeK SM?696e SMK6c 6*Kfe6 46^e66 cq? \q86 SRp=q*4 =6qRKf5Rc KSMRpq*4 qeKf'c6 eq*^6 f*4RpKeI pf\tc6 q5K6e =Rfc4f*^ t6e5Me\q*'6 S6ep6c5 Keft KSfe4 MRK e6cqKfM*pSft \64f'qc t6Mtc6 pt6*4 pSMMK 'RcKRe6 *M? ?f46 cf86cI q?qI S6qK SM?696e B| e6q4 IMR =q*8 f*pf46 pKqeK cf^SK S6q9I pMRKS6e* pR^^6pK =cR6 q=fcfKI ?f56 p6*4 'RK pMRe'6 Mfc =6IM*4 pRttMeK KSMR^SK cM*^ pfK *6? 4696cMt MKS6e p8f* p6'M*4 'c6qe ?6qe RpRqccI \66K pf\tc6 *M*6 5MccM? t6e5Me\ cM? fKp6c5 =RK R*fK f*'cR4f*^ \q*q^6e qtteMq'S ^e6qK Sf^S 5f*q*'fqc =q*8 5f*q*'fqc 5qpK qcc te6pf46*K ?M*46e 5qpK t6Mtc6 f*K6e6pK tRetMp6 qcM*^ 46pf^* 'S6'8 *MK6 ^qp 6*K6e ^q\6 '6*KReI =6'qRp6 tqeKf'Rcqe SRp=q*4 =6Sq9fMe 'Ree6*K pSMRc4 S6qeK M*'6 'M*56e6*'6 KSq* qeMR*4 teMA6'K 4f556e6*'6 ptq'6 ?M*46e f*96pK\6*K ^qp teM^eq\ ^eM?KS tqeKI KM4qI S6 \fpp S6q4 ?M\q* KMKqc c6q46e p6cc 'M*KeMc pKR46*K 5Me^6K qccM? \fppfM* 46'q46 4e6q\ f* 566cf*^ Keq46 e6KRe* 5fc\ pKR46*K \fccfM* pM cqe^6 fppR6 Kf\6 'qcc q9qfcq=c6 p6'KfM* 5Me6f^* f*96pK\6*K ?f46 tM?6e KMKqc pKqI Kq86 KSMR^S tqf*Kf*^ tMcf'6 ?6qe *MKf'6 e6'6*KcI ^eMR*4 f* p6*fMe Sqfe pKqK6\6*K ?Me4 ?SqK 'M\tqe6 e6q4I q'KRqccI 4M?* \Me*f*^ 'S6'8 KM?* 46ptfK6 e65c6'K teM4R'K ?6qtM* qRKSMefKI q*I 56qe MRK pSq86 R*46epKq*4 IMR*^ te6KKI \66Kf*^ ?qe 'qe66e 5fepK =M@ q'KRqccI tf6'6 =6qRKf5Rc 'MRep6 \M9f6 teM4R'K =6K?66* pt6q8 M* e6ptM*p6 tqe6*K te6tqe6 ?SM\ \RpK pf\tc6 q*MKS6e cMM8 p'SMMc pKqeK 5MM4 teM4R'K ^MM4 \qI teM56ppMe 696eIM*6 RtM* =MM8 e6KRe* f*pf46 SM? =MI q^qf* 46'f46 eMM\ e6p6qe'S 6*9feM*\6*Kqc pR^^6pK M* {RfK6 *hK eRc6 =6^f* 'MRc4 5f*4 4Ref*^ e6'Me4 'M*'6e* cMK =eMKS6e Keqf*f*^ 6'M*M\f' MS teM=q=cI p6efMRp 5Me\ pM\6KSf*^ 6*6e^I 5f6c4 \6\=6e 46^e66 =q*8 \fccfM* ^cqpp p'Me6 f*4f'qK6 K6q\ ?fpS *q\6 p\fc6 qe6q cM*^ 6qK 696* 6qpI pSqe6 SMK6c KSq* tMcf'6 4M^ 'qK'S tMpfKfM* 'Sqeq'K6e qRKSMe 4f55f'RcK K6'S*McM^I e6'6*KcI \M96 S6ct M55f'6 pKR4I 'Sq*^6 tef'6 9Mf'6 KSMR^SK pR446*cI KS6fe tqeKI e6\M96 teM=c6\ 4eMt pf\tcI ?6qtM* =6KK6e tqf*Kf*^ q^M R*Kfc eqfp6 =cq'8 5ef6*4 pKqI tqKf6*K 'Sq*^6 pfK6 tMcf'I 'SRe'S ?SMc6 cqI f*pK6q4 KSqK *qKReqc pKeqK6^I e6KRe* eMM\ 5R*4 teM^eq\ q^e66 =fcc tRK 64R'qKfM* 'SMf'6 qcc 'M\tRK6e =65Me6 'c6qe ^eMR*4 pf*'6 e6^fM* pSq86 te6ppRe6 6@t6eK 6c6'KfM* Keqf*f*^ c6q96 cf86cI \q*q^6 K6c69fpfM* ?fcc K6e\ *M? t6q'6 cqpK pKqK6 Kq@ eMq4 ^q\6 86I teM4R'K ^Mqc qKK6*KfM* 'M\6 4qe8 6qK KM^6KS6e pR556e 8*M? ?6 IMRe M55f'fqc 5Me?qe4 pM'f6KI eq4fM cf86 p6e96 5qKS6e 6*6e^I t6epM*qc 'Ree6*K =MKS pf\tcI qeKfpK =f^ 'ef\6 teM96 'M\tqe6 \R'S *6qecI teM4R'KfM* f*5Me\qKfM* Sf^S e64 p6*fMe pR=A6'K qeMR*4 tqeK*6e cfpK =q=I 'M96e q''MR*K f*'e6qp6 4fp'RppfM* pR\\6e pM'fqc \6ppq^6 e6qc SR^6 tqeK*6e ef^SK MS p6e96 q'eMpp 'e6qK6 p668 KMKqc tqI f*5Me\qKfM* ?SMc6 5Rcc ?M\q* MRKpf46 'e6qK6 tqt6e 6@6'RKf96 KSMRpq*4 4f556e6*K 'MpK te6p6*K M5 M*KM 6*4 ^eMRt =6Sq9fMe 5MRe pKq55 6@tcqf* 4M'KMe 'q*4f4qK6 5Me\6e SMK6c \q*I pR556e p6cc 4M?* 'qp6 q=MRK eMM\ 6@t6'K 
\qKK6e 6'M*M\I *Me ?SMc6 5Me^6K pKq^6 '6*Keqc *f'6 p'SMMc pKqK6\6*K 46'fpfM* \6 c6pp =6KK6e =6'M\6 5f*q*'fqc 56? KM*f^SK \qe86K pR446*cI *MK =f^ IMRe qce6q4I pSMeK 36tR=cf'q* e6'6*KcI >\6ef'q* 6*4 ?SM\ pKq^6 S6qcKS cM? qeK pR'S pKqeK 8f*4 fK6\ 'M\tRK6e pKqI pMM* qe^R6 pfpK6e \66K qfe ?SM\ 'qK'S / Rt t6e5Me\q*'6 Sf\ 6pt6'fqccI M5K6* cM*^ ?fKSf* B| t6e5Me\q*'6 pM\6M*6 K6q'S 6*9feM*\6*K KeRKS f*K6e*qKfM*qc \f*RK6 Keqf*f*^ 696*K pR\\6e 4M p6@Rqc 'q* *6?p 6qpK =Rfc4 M?*6e ?eM*^ 'qe e6qc \M46e* \64f'qc pKq55 e6'Me4 K6*4 S6e pt6*4 KM 'fKI e6qccI c6q4 q'K eM'8 696* Fe p696eqc 5MM4 M55f'6e 'M*pR\6e \qeefq^6 696eIKSf*^ =q^ p6@Rqc 5MccM? \6*KfM* Mt6eqKfM* 6@q\tc6 \f*RK6 t6efM4 5f*qccI 5fe6 tMcf'6 e6ptM*pf=fcfKI 'RpKM\6e / p'6*6 KSMRpq*4 p6*4 pR''6pp5Rc ?efK6e 5f*4 e6pRcK e6\qf* cf6 Sq96 pKqK6 B| 4fp'Rpp e6'6*K 'f9fc M*KM =6'M\6 \MKS6e q?qI *hK MKS6e 46'fpfM* 'M\\R*fKI KeMR=c6 qcc f*'cR46 pRe6 \R'S tMtRcqe 'MpK \f*4 \qI e6'6f96 KS6p6 pSqe6 ^eMRt 'SMMp6 46'f46 \qAMe eq'6 tMcfKf'qc cqI \6q* 4eq? 6q'S t6q'6 KSe6qK 5cI ?qK'S *Me f*K6e*qKfM*qc p6q 46Kqfc f\teM96 e6'M^*fD6 ^e66* *f^SK q'eMpp 'M*pR\6e \I >\6ef'q* \q*q^6\6*K teM56ppfM*qc 6cp6 cM96 qeMR*4 tSIpf'qc qp8 pSqe6 tqeKI pKqK6 SMRp6 I6p q*MKS6e 5f*^6e pKMe6 \q*q^6\6*K tf'KRe6 =M@ 5M'Rp 4f6 pKR55 q'KRqccI *6?p IMR KIt6 pKeM*^ ?S6KS6e 'Mq'S eqKS6e pKR46*K eMq4 \Rpf' 'SMf'6 tcqI pMR*4 q''MR*K e6'6*K 'Sqe^6 teM=c6\ KIt6 pMRKS SMc4 pt6*4 e6qpM* pM\6KSf*^ 4fp'Rpp qcM*^ 46ptfK6 =6 f\q^f*6 46=qK6 ?SMp6 *6@K pf*^c6 =6K?66* 46=qK6 IMR 5qpK pKMeI e6cqK6 AM= AM= eM'8 5fe6 qp8 fK cMp6 'cqpp SqttI =I *696e te6tqe6 tqKf6*K AM= 5f*6 MRK \MRKS pKMe6 5fe\ 'cMp6 9MK6 *M pM\6=M4I 655MeK Ke66 KSMR^SK MttMeKR*fKI ^eMRt tMMe ?Me8 'S6'8 ^6*6eqc MRK 4656*p6 ?6f^SK fKp pKfcc KS6I *M? Kefqc Keq4fKfM*qc \fppfM* =6Sq9fMe tMpfKfM* 'SMMp6 S6e c6q46e pMc4f6e \M9f6 e6ptM*p6 *MK6 'Mcc6^6 pt66'S 696*K 5eM*K pM c6q96 pR''6pp 6*9feM*\6*K qc?qIp 5ef6*4 4fe6'KfM* q*IKSf*^ ^M SMRe p'Me6 Ke6qK q=M96 5Me 46pf^* cMK Sq*4 =cR6 =Rpf*6pp p'Me6 Sq96 ?f56 \Me*f*^ *696e \6 'MReK 'f9fc 4qe8 e6ptM*pf=fcfKI 5fcc 4qe8 tqeKf'ftq*K Ke66 AM= ?fKSf* q*f\qc cfpK ?SMc6 f*'cR4f*^ 69f46*'6 ?fcc ?M\q* I6qS ?MeeI 5qcc \q*q^6\6*K 'M*pf46e pKe66K ?qcc pf46 te6KKI tqe6*K cf86cI te6KKI q*4 696*K =cq'8 KSMRpq*4 ^M 'RK teM=q=cI 96eI 4qKq ^eM? =RK 6556'K c6q4 pfK q^qf* \qI=6 5Me'6 'q\tqf^* cf56 9f'Kf\ q4RcK 4f556e6*'6 qcpM 'M*56e6*'6 ?f* *696e \M\6*K 'qe66e p6qK =f^ 4ef96 4f**6e 5Me?qe4 c6^qc =fccfM* cf*6 \qI=6 5q'KMe pSMMK 'M\tqe6 566c K6cc KS6* t6e5Me\q*'6 4f**6e pIpK6\ KSeMR^SMRK M5 pSMRc4 pR556e tMpfKf96 cfKKc6 e6ptM*pf=fcfKI fK q44e6pp pKfcc pRe6 MttMeKR*fKI '6cc 866t qccM? p6*p6 pf46 46p'ef=6 SfpKMeI SR^6 =6KK6e p8fcc tMtRcqe 6*K6e 'fKfD6* 6'M*M\I Sq*^ \qe86K SRp=q*4 cM*^ SfK pR446*cI ^R* ?f56 8*M? =fccfM* p6'RefKI 5Me?qe4 f*96pK\6*K =65Me6 S6 ?SM =MKS \MKS6e \fcfKqeI S6ct *6qecI =6qK S6qcKS t6q'6 tRcc cMp6 qp8 *6K?Me8 S6q4 Keq46 \6\=6e ?6pK Sqtt6* 64^6 KSq*8 *M? KM^6KS6e f*4RpKeI Keqf*f*^ t6eSqtp c6q46e 5RKRe6 5e66 =65Me6 tqf*Kf*^ 8f4 q^qf* Mc4 teM=q=cI KeRKS pR556e 'Sqfe fK \M46e* pt6'fqc pKR4I cq*4 f*5Me\qKfM* =Mqe4 t6epM* \MpK e6\M96 e6cqK6 Mfc M55 fK 'qeeI 5fepK f*K6e6pK qp p6@ KMKqc q*f\qc q4\fK q4\fK 'S6'8 Sq*^ 466t t6e S6ct ?qe \6q* \MpK 'ef\6 q^e66\6*K cqI =R4^6K 'qtfKqc M''Re 6fKS6e 5fpS 'RK 56qe \M\6*K pfD6 pKqI p8f* 'MR*KeI 'M*KeMc c6^qc K6* 696eIKSf*^ 4M?* 'SRe'S 'M*4fKfM* KSe66 pR''6pp cqK6 RpRqccI ?Me4 6f^SK R*46e eM'8 p66 5RKRe6 R*46e pq56 ?qc8 SR*4e64 *6K?Me8 'SMf'6 'qp6 pKMe6 f*pf46 eMq4 tqeK*6e 'M\6 tqKK6e* cf*6 5qe ?6qe tef9qK6 Sfp e6KRe* e6KRe* RtM* pf\tc6 =6 4ef96 p6*fMe =Rfc4 te6ppRe6 p6@ =e6q8 pR''6pp5Rc Sf^S \fccfM* KeI f*pK6q4 qeMR*4 pKR55 *6qe tMtRcqe 5fepK ?6 M*KM IMRe Fep t6e M*cI pKqKfM* J6\M'eqK Ke66 q44 \6qpRe6 t6q'6 pKMe6 efp8 5Me6f^* \MpK M*'6 Ke6qK\6*K MKS6ep tqpp e696qc e6cf^fMRp 46qc ?M\q* '6eKqf*cI fKp =q*8 ^eM? cM? p'SMMc Rp 6I6 q^qf*pK 6556'K \6\MeI 'M*pR\6e tqf*Kf*^ te6ppRe6 6'M*M\I p6e96 6pt6'fqccI 5MMK pM\6KSf*^ pKIc6 q\MR*K cfKKc6 \qKK6e e6qccI q'Kf9fKI 4f55f'RcK ?f56 =q*8 p66\ 'RK 'ef\6 =RI =qcc 'Sq*'6 q44e6pp =q*8 4eMt c6qpK 46qc e6\6\=6e tMtRcqKfM* cMpp 5cMMe c6^ pKMt pSM? q44 tMcfKf'p M?*6e 6@t6ef6*'6 8*M?c64^6 KS6e6 =Rfc4 te6tqe6 \f^SK 6@q\tc6 \MRKS KMKqc pKeM*^ p6*p6 pSqe6 Sqe4 'M*Kf*R6 \f*RK6 KeMR=c6 \q86 4qI KM4qI 5f^SK eqfp6 =e6q8 4Ref*^ cq*^Rq^6 Sq*4 'M\tRK6e 56qe ?MeeI e6pRcK qKK6*KfM* ^M pKeM*^ *6qecI pKeR'KRe6 e6'6*KcI eqK6 tqKf6*K q'Kf9fKI *6?p qe6q SRp=q*4 KM p6qpM* *6?ptqt6e tMpfKfM* 'qp6 qRKSMefKI \M46e* p6@ 6*MR^S 'q*4f4qK6 =qe 6*K6e 5RKRe6 *f'6 9qcR6 5RKRe6 efp8 *MeKS ?Me8 Sf\ *MeKS pKIc6 p696* 'Sq*^6 *6'6ppqeI '6eKqf*cI e6qpM* qS6q4 SMK ?S6e6 S6qK qeKf'c6 8*M? M*KM tqeKf'ftq*K K?M Rp6 q\M*^ c6K =6KK6e p6*fMe pIpK6\ 4f556e6*K cfpK6* teM4R'KfM* *Me ?SqK qce6q4I q''6tK R*Kfc e696qc pMRKS6e* cfpK6* 5f*4 SR\q* pKeR'KRe6 Ke6qK \qAMefKI \66Kf*^ e6cqK6 f*96pK\6*K 6'M*M\I 36tR=cf'q* q^M pMM* Me^q*fDqKfM* pf^* SfpKMeI =f^ 4f556e6*K *664 \RpK qKKq'8 eqfp6 56qe 'M96e pKR46*K qR4f6*'6 q\MR*K 4fp'M96e *6? AM= ?f*4M? cM*^ =6IM*4 tf'KRe6 5fpS 'Sq*'6 teM56ppfM*qc q^qf*pK e6qc pt66'S p6'RefKI qfe pfK ^f96 e6'6*KcI pM\6=M4I e6{Rfe6 ?Me86e \qAMefKI 4f55f'RcK \64f'qc f*pf46 f\teM96 qeMR*4 tMcfKf'p \MRKS 6@t6'K pM\6 ?Me86e qcM*^ qRKSMefKI 566c 4fe6'KMe eq*^6 cMpp q=M96 \qe86K fKp *6K?Me8 ?S6* 'Sqe^6 c65K Kefqc \RpK e6ptM*4 \qK6efqc 36tR=cf'q* \M96 M55f'6e pKeqK6^I S6q9I 'cMp6 \6\=6e pMeK pMRKS6e* IMRe =6^f* MRKpf46 =6KK6e t6e5Me\ =6Sq9fMe *696e ^6K {RfK6 M*KM 5fepK 5f^Re6 pKfcc SMK6c t6Mtc6 pM KSfe4 'fKfD6* \6*KfM* teM'6pp 6*MR^S M''Re 5Rcc e65c6'K \66Kf*^ eMq4 q=c6 =cq'8 tqI p'6*6 qcKSMR^S 6qecI 4qR^SK6e te6ppRe6 tSM*6 e6'6*K eqfp6 Keq96c cq? S6qe \Me6 =6*65fK cqK6 'Sq*'6 6@6'RKf96 t6eSqtp cf86 Mt6* B| pKqe \MpK ?eM*^ p6e9f'6 6@q'KcI qRKSMefKI Kefqc qp8 =q4 Keq96c \6q* c6^qc 8f4 5R*4 5MMK \f*RK6 'M*KeMc ?S6* 'M\tqe6 ;F 6*9feM*\6*Kqc ?qcc ?6qtM* 
5Me'6 f*K6e6pKf*^ eq'6 f*4f'qK6 696eI=M4I p6e9f'6 q^M 4qKq 64^6 \f*4 'q\6eq ?S6e6 Keft SRp=q*4 q*I pf\tc6 c6K 5f*4 =64 teM4R'K 6@6'RKf96 =q*8 'MR*KeI 9fpfK 5Me^6K =MM8 tqf*Kf*^ 46^e66 tcq'6 q4\fK 'M\6 ?f*4M? eq4fM KM?qe4 5q'6 'qe6 I6qe \qK6efqc pMeK *MK 'Ree6*K f*K6e9f6? qcc ?qK'S \qAMefKI K6q\ ^fec ?SI S6qK p696eqc tqeK*6e eqKS6e cfpK q*qcIpfp ?SM\ tqf*Kf*^ R*Kfc 5Me'6 6f^SK 5qpK pfpK6e pKR4I KSf*8 q''MR*K KS6 cfKKc6 pMc4f6e qRKSMe \qeefq^6 ?SM\ pKq*4qe4 teM56ppMe pq56 \R'S 4ef96 teMA6'K KM^6KS6e pKR55 I6qe tef9qK6 =6'qRp6 qcM*^ te6pf46*K c6pp e6'Me4 tRetMp6 c6qpK pMM* tf'KRe6 eq*^6 tMtRcqKfM* ?6f^SK pf@ qR4f6*'6 46=qK6 ?fKS 'M*'6e* 5f*fpS 566c q=MRK cf56 q*4 SfpKMeI 6*6e^I *MK qtteMq'S KeR6 pKR46*K q'eMpp 'fKfD6* MttMeKR*fKI 4f55f'RcK pf*^c6 fK6\ q''MR*K p6ef6p 'M*4fKfM* e6KRe* tM?6e 5f^Re6 =RI qK 696* ^e6qK cqpK ?qK6e Sqfe te696*K 'M\\6e'fqc tqKf6*K e6^fM* e6p6qe'S tMtRcqe 'M*pR\6e M55f'6e pR=A6'K 5qKS6e 'fKI efp8 KeR6 ef^SK tcqI zM*^e6pp q''Me4f*^ \fcfKqeI KSMp6 AM= K6c69fpfM* KSf*^ K6q'S6e 5ef6*4 Ke6qK\6*K pfKRqKfM* 5q'6 ?f*4 ^6*6eqKfM* ?fcc tqf* ?eM*^ 6'M*M\f' KSMRpq*4 =q4 *6qecI M* 9qefMRp 5Me KSMp6 c6K eMM\ Sq*4 p6@ 'Sqeq'K6e teM4R'K f46q 'c6qecI teM96 pKqK6 KSfp =6KK6e zM*^e6pp 'qe 'M*pf46e 5f6c4 tqe6*K 5qKS6e 4fe6'KfM* cMK 'MRc4 46'fpfM* Kf\6 \q^qDf*6 6@q'KcI 8f*4 tf'KRe6 M5K6* KM4qI tMtRcqKfM* q'K MtKfM* 4eR^ 'qe6 q\M*^ S6q9I 4eR^ 696* Kqp8 e6cqKfM*pSft SR*4e64 fK6\ c6q96 =6KK6e p'f6*KfpK tMf*K 5Me6f^* 'e6qK6 pfK6 =f^ 566c tMtRcqKfM* pM*^ 696eIM*6 5qpK pMR*4 q^6 =6*65fK S6q4 eRc6 696*f*^ tqt6e teM4R'6 q556'K c6^qc p\qcc 5q\fcI f\teM96 KSf*^ \66Kf*^ ?Me4 SM\6 KMKqc fKp =MI ?6qe \qe86K 'q\6eq tMf*K qp pSM? tcq'6 \qAMe c65K q\M*^ e6te6p6*K 6I6 ?fKSMRK Keq4fKfM*qc ptef*^ 4e6q\ ?6pK6e* teM4R'KfM* ?SqK696e =6cf696 ?S6* pM* ?f56 Ke66 q'eMpp \f^SK tR=cf' tMpfKfM* teM4R'K teM4R'6 S6 *q\6 5qcc pqI f*96pK\6*K KS6\ teM=c6\ p6@ =fcc pKeM*^ SM?696e 56? e6q4I 6*9feM*\6*Kqc 6@q'KcI q44 KS6* eM'8 q*IKSf*^ ?fcc *qKRe6 =6pK f*4RpKeI e6^fM* KS6I 'M*Kqf* M96e K6'S*McM^I ?efK6e tMtRcqKfM* *q\6 6*9feM*\6*K p6q e6q4 S6qe ^eMRt Rp tqeKI ?SqK696e 6qecI KS6I =fK =fcc 4eq? 'Sqe^6 ?f46 cM'qc 5eM*K pf*'6 IMR*^ =RI Kf\6 ^RI KS6* Me46e q4RcK 4696cMt\6*K teM=c6\ 46'q46 tqKK6e* pMRKS q\MR*K =64 e6ptM*4 'M\tqe6 pKeM*^ ?f46 f* qcc qppR\6 eMM\ p696eqc J6\M'eqK e6q4I f*4RpKeI q*I tqf*Kf*^ 46Kqfc =Rfc4f*^ c6K M*'6 p66\ 4ef96 6*9feM*\6*Kqc MKS6e ^f96 'S6'8 tef9qK6 SR^6 cM? 'c6qe SfK 5Me?qe4 SfK KS6e6 qeK =6^f* Kq@ ^fec Mt6* pSq86 4fp'RppfM* =qcc c6qpK *6?ptqt6e SM\6 Keqf*f*^ 4fp'Rpp S6ct 696eIKSf*^ 5fe\ pt6'fqc S6q9I ^qp f*'cR46 q*I ^6*6eqc pSMeK RpRqccI 'e6qK6 qtteMq'S 6@q'KcI tf'8 p6K =6K?66* K6q'S pMeK K6* e6\qf* Kqc8 tMcf'6 6f^SK ?f56 tMpfKfM* tM?6e I6qS e6q4I 'M*KeMc \6*KfM* M*cI pSMRc4 cq*4 ?6cc 5Me 4fe6'KMe S6q4 tcqI M96e \fppfM* ^M96e*\6*K KS6* q''6tK pKeR'KRe6 5ef6*4 6@6'RKf96 566c q=M96 qKK6*KfM* =q*8 pKeM*^ qeK =65Me6 SM?696e tcqI6e 5R*4 KeI e6q'S fK 8f*4 ef^SK R*46epKq*4 \Rpf' ef^SK 9MK6 *M ^R6pp teM^eq\ \6\MeI 6@tcqf* 5Me?qe4 =65Me6 KS6e6 p66\ ptq'6 M*'6 cf56 f*96pK\6*K 'M*KeMc q'eMpp q*IM*6 '6eKqf*cI 4f55f'RcK *696e I6K ef'S Sq*4 p\fc6 MRKpf46 'M\tq*I cf56 qttcI ^e66* pKq*4 '6eKqf* 'M*KeMc S6ep6c5 cq*4 'SMMp6 qeKf'c6 q^e66\6*K cf56 qce6q4I 5eM*K M55f'fqc *MeKS 696eI=M4I I6K \6q* 5Me ?S6KS6e f* M?* pKeqK6^I KM*f^SK p6@ *qKReqc 'RcKReqc 5Me6f^* ?S6* tM?6e =q^ 8*M?c64^6 q*IKSf*^ p6efMRp RpRqccI 4ef96 fKp 5RKRe6 KM?qe4 MKS6e 46\M'eqKf' 'Mc4 q''Me4f*^ f*KM 'M\tq*I c6^ ^R6pp f*'cR4f*^ 'Mq'S teM4R'K pMR*4 5Rcc Mt6eqKfM* tM?6e *qKfM*qc 4f**6e teM56ppfM*qc ?S6* zM*^e6pp \q*I 566c 6c6'KfM* 6@fpK KSeM? tRK =qcc 5fe6 'RcKRe6 p696eqc pR^^6pK pf^*f5f'q*K ?6qe KM4qI qcKSMR^S e6ptM*pf=fcfKI p696* KM4qI 4696cMt\6*K eMM\ 5fc\ p6@Rqc 'qK'S pf\tcI cqR^S ^eM? 'McMe qc\MpK 566cf*^ AMf* 6*9feM*\6*Kqc M*'6 \66K \qKK6e cq*4 RtM* 5Rcc efp8 pKq55 \MKS6e pt6'fqc 5qKS6e 'qe 5646eqc 'M*pR\6e tf'KRe6 'Rt f*5Me\qKfM* 'MReK teM=c6\ Me Mt6eqKfM* KS6I R*46epKq*4 \qK6efqc 'qcc ?Sf'S f*K6e*qKfM*qc p6e9f'6 M''Re q'Kf9fKI pKR46*K cf96 =6qK =RK KM?qe4 tMpfKfM* e6ptM*pf=fcfKI 5Me\ f*'e6qp6 4fe6'KfM* q'Kf9fKI 46q4 pR''6pp5Rc qeKfpK p6'RefKI I6K \fcfKqeI p6cc 4f556e6*'6 \fppfM* ^6*6eqc 6@t6'K Keq46 pf46 tqeK cMpp MRe 36tR=cf'q* pR=A6'K 'ef\6 f*9Mc96 q*I 46pf^* tqe6*K 46qc IMR ?SqK q5K6e pRe5q'6 4fe6'KfM* =e6q8 *6K?Me8 tMppf=c6 KSf*8 \M*KS KeMR=c6 'RcKReqc 5MM4 pMR*4 eqK6 =RK pR556e 5f^SK qe6q K6e\ 696*K KS6p6 6*9feM*\6*K qccM? ?S6KS6e qKK6*KfM* 'M\\M* 'qRp6 *6@K q*MKS6e \fcfKqeI tcq*K KM?* 4f6 te6pf46*K pKe66K ?qI \6\MeI ?6 pR=A6'K ?qK6e \R'S fKp6c5 ?SMp6 ^RI cf^SK S6e \qK6efqc ^qp ^qp \RpK 6qpI fppR6 4qR^SK6e =fcc t6eSqtp 'q\tqf^* 6q'S S6e f*K6e*qKfM*qc *f'6 Fe *MK6 qKKMe*6I qeMR*4 e64 pR'S 'MRtc6 f*pK6q4 =qcc Mfc 5eM\ fKp cq*^Rq^6 5M'Rp 'Mq'S f\tq'K pf*^ pf*^c6 566c pMeK qtt6qe =fK ?6pK6e* Me46e =q*8 f*96pK\6*K *M? f\tMeKq*K \q*q^6\6*K ?668 =6 {RqcfKI ?6qtM* I6qe ^cqpp =Mqe4 \f^SK 5Me6f^* *q\6 46=qK6 >\6ef'q* Sqtt6* e6q4I '6*K6e qRKSMe p6qK pKqKfM* e6KRe* cf96 46qKS \66Kf*^ KMKqc *6'6ppqeI 'MRtc6 ?MRc4 5qe ?SMc6 ?Me8 4eMt 6*MR^S \M*KS cf6 ^eMR*4 e6pMRe'6 \64f'qc ?f*4 pMM* f*KM tcq* 4fp6qp6 ?fpS 655MeK t6epM* Ke6qK\6*K pKqe =cq'8 'cqpp pf\tc6 *Me pfD6 'q\tqf^* ;F e6te6p6*K pt6'fqc KM^6KS6e e6KRe* ?M*46e K6* cM*^ pKqK6\6*K ^R6pp 5qpK ?668 K6'S*McM^I \qAMefKI \M46e* cqK6e tcq*K SMK6c {RqcfKI q44e6pp 6@q'KcI tMcf'6 =65Me6 q\MR*K KMKqc *qKRe6 5Me\6e 'SMMp6 8f4 R*Kfc KM?* Sq96 e6pK =6 696*K ?Sfc6 5f*^6e 696*f*^ SMK6c p6e96 4fp6qp6 pKeR'KRe6 c6KK6e pKMt 5M'Rp 5MRe pMRKS6e* 5qKS6e ?efK6e ^Mqc p6ef6p 'cMp6 p\qcc '6*KReI SMt6 pKfcc t6e5Me\ 655MeK tqI KSf*^ e6cqKfM*pSft ^eMRt 'Ree6*K efp8 'M\\M* 'RK pMc4f6e KSMp6 4fp'RppfM* 4fp6qp6 46'q46 te6pf46*K pfKRqKfM* 5f*fpS pR''6pp cqK6e \qI=6 p'6*6 ptef*^ 9fpfK eq4fM f\q^6 tMpfKf96 I6qS KSeM? 'M\6 =64 te6p6*K =f^ *qKRe6 S6 pMeK 69f46*'6 ^q\6 \M\6*K =q*8 4fp'Rpp te6tqe6 Iqe4 \M9f6 pt6*4 696eIKSf*^ qKKq'8 5qpK qp8 cM? 'M*Kf*R6 tMppf=c6 t6epM*qc ?MeeI =MI tMcf'6 =qe ?SM tMf*K pSMeK pR\\6e 5Me^6K e6qc ?fKSf* tcq* MS / 4eR^ 5f96 p6*p6 =qp6 AMf* 5Me^6K =Me* KSe6qK teM'6pp 46Kqfc 46\M'eqKf' p\qcc Keft 4fp'RppfM* ptMeK 5R*4 Iqe4 ?fKS =64 f*pKfKRKfM* tqpp 4f**6e q*qcIpfp qRKSMe tcqI 4fe6'KMe 4M c6q96 pM\6KSf*^ ?S6* 5f*6 MRe 'q*'6e 'SMf'6 =ef*^ R*Kfc 696* 'M*4fKfM* 'qcc t6e5Me\q*'6 9MK6 eqfp6 qKKq'8 6f^SK pSMRc4 5q\fcI 'SRe'S *6K?Me8 ^R* KMR^S S6qK *6'6ppqeI 5f*^6e cMpp KIt6 t6Mtc6 MRKpf46 pSMK 'M\tRK6e pMRKS6e* KSe6qK e6\M96 ?qe 5Me'6 4MMe KS6p6 ^R* e696qc tMcfKf'p \qKK6e \qe86K 'M*'6e* t6Mtc6 =RK pRe5q'6 ?fKSMRK 'McMe 6qK ^cqpp ?eM*^ \RpK f\tq'K q*f\qc pMRe'6 ?qe 696eIKSf*^ M8 qce6q4I f*K6e6pK pR446*cI Sfp M*cI cqI 5f*q*'fqc 5f96 4eMt \q^qDf*6 fppR6 qe6q 5fe6 ^6K e6q4 'q\tqf^* S6qe q44 'M*pR\6e KM4qI 'SMf'6 \M46c c65K 6f^SK pSq86 teM56ppfM*qc e6q4I *696e KM?qe4 p6efMRp Sqe4 'qK'S p6q ^eM?KS e6\qf* f*pKfKRKfM* cMK c6qpK SMt6 *6?ptqt6e teM9f46 KSfe4 5f^Re6 5646eqc eMc6 'c6qe \Ip6c5 tRK =MM8 ?668 KM te696*K 9qcR6 pq56 *6K?Me8 ^MM4 655MeK *M ^Mqc f*96pK\6*K =eMKS6e pKqKfM* Sf^S pR''6pp *q\6 M*KM qcpM =qp6 p6ef6p =q=I =6Sf*4 *MKSf*^ q*IKSf*^ =6K?66* 'q*4f4qK6 f*'cR46 64^6 'M\\R*fKI f*pf46 pM'f6KI 46qc t6e5Me\ qc?qIp *MK6 6fKS6e 6@t6'K p\qcc 'qcc 5qfc teM96 q^e66\6*K SMRe pKqe cMp6 'MReK teMA6'K q^qf* p6qpM* tqpp 4fp6qp6 *M? \fccfM* =fK \M46e* cqR^S ?efK6 KSRp q*f\qc Rt 4fp'RppfM* fK p\fc6 f*K6e9f6? 5f*qccI MRe \qAMe pKfcc e6q'S f*4f9f4Rqc tMcfKf'p R*Kfc f*4f'qK6 e6p6qe'S cf86 \qI =6*65fK \6KSM4 'SRe'S MttMeKR*fKI \q*q^6e eq*^6 fK ?SqK696e \Ip6c5 qfe f*KM f\tq'K KMM \Ip6c5 'Sqeq'K6e f*9Mc96 pf*^c6 Sfp =6cf696 qfe *6K?Me8 KM?* t6q'6 J6\M'eqK Rt f*pK6q4 MRKpf46 4e6q\ qce6q4I =qp6 'c6qe 6pKq=cfpS 6*AMI teMA6'K =6'M\6 pq\6 e6\M96 q*IM*6 t6eSqtp 'M*'6e* e6'6*K SMc4 5fcc efp8 p6ef6p q9Mf4 'Ree6*K Keq46 \6\=6e 4M?* \qf*Kqf* pMR*4 te6ppRe6 q*MKS6e tcqI6e 'qe4 KM^6KS6e pKq*4qe4 qeKf'c6 46qc *6qecI te696*K q5K6e q9qfcq=c6 4qKq SfK \M9f6 q*f\qc pM\6M*6 \fccfM* teMt6eKI q'K pIpK6\ \qKK6e 6*9feM*\6*K 'M\\6e'fqc cfpK q556'K p'Me6 KSMp6 \q'Sf*6 pR'S tqe6*K tMppf=c6 qeKfpK 696eIKSf*^ pSMeK 'q\6eq \66K qce6q4I 'e6qK6 pKMt 'M\\M* pfpK6e \qe86K tcq*K pR\\6e ef'S f*'cR46 *qKfM* =q^ 46=qK6 ^eMRt cfKKc6 f*5Me\qKfM* cM*^ '6*K6e *MK \6q* SR*4e64 te6pf46*K tMtRcqe teM=c6\ Ke66 I6K e6'6f96 p6@ f* 5646eqc 'MRtc6 qcc q*4 M?* pKfcc KRe* pR446*cI ^eMRt tqeK \fpp 6@t6'K e6qccI 6qK M* 4fp'Rpp f*4664 f\tq'K ^RI SMRe SRp=q*4 f*'cR46 pKfcc q*p?6e M?* =qe pf*^ \66K 696e Mt6* qc?qIp 'Sqcc6*^6 pR556e teq'Kf'6 4qe8 \R'S p'SMMc te6p6*K pqI *M*6 q*I 'q*'6e 6'M*M\I 4f6 Ke6qK\6*K =M4I qeMR*4 p'Me6 *MK 5q'6 qK RpRqccI MKS6ep ?efK6e SM? p'SMMc K6*4 teM9f46 4fe6'KMe 'M*'6e* Keqf*f*^ pf\tcI KM tMpfKfM* tMtRcqKfM* cf96 c6pp p6K tf'KRe6 'RK 'ef\6 S6qcKS KS6e6 Ke6qK q*I ?qc8 46=qK6 46Kqfc =ef*^ =eMKS6e *hK \qI 46qKS 46pf^* f*K6e*qKfM*qc 6@tcqf* pf^*f5f'q*K Keft 46'q46 566c qfe e6pK \66Kf*^ 9MK6 MKS6ep 'M\6 5ef6*4 MRK e6pMRe'6 pM'fqc c6qpK M?* qc?qIp ?Me8 ^eMR*4 96eI eR* *696e 6*K6e ^e6qK 4eR^ 'M\\R*fKI ?6 5qe ?MRc4 6cp6 ?Sfc6 q4RcK =6Sq9fMe q'KfM* \M96\6*K p8fcc 8fK'S6* ?Mec4 KMR^S 8f*4 fK6\ *hK *hK q^6*'I 6*AMI ?fKSMRK 6@q'KcI 5qpK SfK e6ptM*p6 696* Keft ?qe qc\MpK =fK 6*MR^S e6ptM*p6 'M*Kf*R6 fK =f^ eqKS6e pf*'6 t6eSqtp t6Mtc6 4fp'RppfM* >\6ef'q* 56qe tSM*6 6*AMI p'Me6 pfK ?Me4 ^f96 c6q4 =6Sq9fMe qe^R6 ?Sfc6 pSMRc4 p'f6*'6 696*f*^ 6@t6'K 'M*pR\6e e6cqKfM*pSft =fK p6*4 ^eMR*4 J6\M'eqK 4f556e6*K 5MRe teMA6'K KSMRpq*4 pSMRc4 S6ct pSMMK cf56 ?qK6e I6p e6\qf* =q*8 \Me6 eR* pf\tcI pKqe tqeK*6e 5Me\6e ^eM? *6K?Me8 tRcc zM*^e6pp 5f*q*'fqc 5f*q*'fqc 'M96e p'6*6 \q'Sf*6 =RK 'qe4 6*MR^S \q*q^6\6*K S6q9I 5qKS6e ?668 q^qf* e6'6*KcI ^e6qK 5qpK pt66'S tqpp 4fe6'KfM* \R'S pR'S tMtRcqe f\q^6 pM\6Kf\6p 5f*fpS 'q* {R6pKfM* S6qeK 'M\\6e'fqc q'KRqccI ?f56 ?efK6e 5f*qc qe\ *MK \f*4 p6qpM* qKKq'8 cMp6 5fe6 ?efK6 p8f* ef'S fppR6 M55 p8fcc Kefqc 'qtfKqc M8 'MR*KeI K?M *qKfM*qc cf86cI Sq*4 =6pK Rp 'M*Kqf* tMtRcqKfM* f*pK6q4 pRe5q'6 eMc6 f*96pK\6*K pKIc6 c6q4 IMRep6c5 56qe cM'qc p6cc tRetMp6 zM*^e6pp 5fe\ f*4f'qK6 4f556e6*K ?MeeI qRKSMefKI 4fp6qp6 K6e\ IMR f*5Me\qKfM* ?MRc4 pSMRc4 6@q\tc6 5RKRe6 p668 5MccM? 4MMe ^Mqc 'SMf'6 c696c 5RKRe6 =M4I 9f'Kf\ \q*q^6 M55 cM*^ q4\f*fpKeqKfM* ?qI 5Me\ pKM'8 *qKRe6 e6'6*K 'M*Kf*R6 cf*6 MRKpf46 q\M*^ ?6qe KeI p6'M*4 cq*^Rq^6 R*fK ?f56 AM= 
Sqe4 tcq'6 p'f6*KfpK q=c6 ^eMRt p8fcc q=fcfKI tRcc e6'M^*fD6 5Me\6e tq^6 \M9f6 SR^6 5f^Re6 5q\fcI Sqfe cfpK6* *M? 5cI tM?6e S6q9I 'e6qK6 tMpfKf96 f*'e6qp6 pR=A6'K Sq*4 =6Sf*4 64^6 tqe6*K Keq46 KSMR^SK Kq86 'Sq*^6 q^6*K pKMe6 =6K?66* ^qp 5f*qccI 4qR^SK6e e6pMRe'6 q^6*'I \64fq 'Mq'S cf86cI 4f556e6*'6 pSq86 'RcKRe6 \Ip6c5 tMcfKf'p ?fcc qRKSMefKI 5646eqc cfpK *q\6 tqpK q=fcfKI 6'M*M\I pM\6=M4I \Me*f*^ cfpK 4f6 'M\tRK6e f* MRK tR=cf' 'SMf'6 Me^q*fDqKfM* 5Me'6 teM^eq\ 6fKS6e =q'8 qRKSMefKI / S6qK cMp6 p8fcc ?qfK \qK6efqc tf'8 'MpK qp R*Kfc f*K6e*qKfM*qc ?SfK6 4656*p6 q^qf* pSM? ?f*4 eqK6 cM? =qp6 q?qI M*cI ?eM*^ AMf* ?fcc pKR55 e6q4I Kq86 KM?qe4 \Ip6c5 '6*K6e pKfcc 'qcc ?S6* 466t pt6'f5f' ?qcc M*cI KeMR=c6 AM= ?qcc 86I q''Me4f*^ ?fpS 5MM4 S6q9I ?qcc pfpK6e 'qtfKqc \6 SM? 'ef\6 Me^q*fDqKfM* 5qcc e6qpM* *6?p 6c6'KfM* cqI qtteMq'S M?*6e 696* pRttMeK =65Me6 \M96 ^6*6eqc =qcc 5fpS 466t 'q\6eq pKfcc 5Me\6e f\tq'K \M*KS ?fcc p\fc6 q*qcIpfp pMRKS =Rpf*6pp qcc 4fe6'KMe \64fq pRe5q'6 \6*KfM* S6e 5MM4 e6te6p6*K pKqK6\6*K ?MRc4 e6pK pKM'8 =Rfc4 I6K f*K6e*qKfM*qc SMRe =qcc pSMRc46e te696*K e6cf^fMRp ?qe \fcfKqeI M5 {RfK6 KM cfKKc6 6556'K tMMe ?MeeI ?qcc 8*M?c64^6 e6^fM* tqeKf'ftq*K 696eIM*6 9f6? eq'6 5fpS p\fc6 tf'KRe6 Rt \qf* KSMp6 ?qc8 5MRe tMcf'I pSMeK 5fe6 teM56ppMe 6*6e^I 6I6 tf'8 SR\q* 'S6'8 \fccfM* f* ^Mqc pM\6=M4I cqK6 'Mcc6^6 qeMR*4 p668 *696e tMcf'6 MRK 'M*'6e* ^eM?KS \f*4 qp t6q'6 ^6*6eqc p668 q''6tK \q* SMptfKqc 'Sq*'6 c696c Keq96c fKp qcM*^ 'M\\6e'fqc ?efK6e 4M'KMe 6\tcMI66 e6'6*KcI 'q\tqf^* \Me*f*^ te6ppRe6 KSe6qK Keq96c 'q*'6e q=MRK 8*M?c64^6 46'f46 *R\=6e KS6MeI IMRep6c5 tMpfKfM* \qeefq^6 c6KK6e qp8 
Sf\p6c5 q\MR*K 6qpI ^MM4 cq? 5f6c4 \Ip6c5 q^qf* 696*f*^ Mt6eqKfM* c6pp 5Me^6K pKe66K 6@t6eK 9qefMRp qeMR*4 ptMeK p6'RefKI 46q4 pf\tc6 5cMMe c6q4 'MR*KeI 5Me^6K qKK6*KfM* SMRe f*'cR4f*^ q=c6 p\fc6 SR*4e64 ?Mec4 M556e cfpK KM4qI tqeKf'ftq*K 4eR^ KSeMR^SMRK pMRe'6 cqK6e *6@K tqeKf'ftq*K 'M\\M* t6Mtc6 =qe 4f556e6*'6 Sf^S 96eI SqttI 'q\tqf^* \MpK \64f'qc pfpK6e tRK pt6*4 eR* K6pK tcq* ?f*4 c696c KS6MeI MttMeKR*fKI pt6q8 cMp6 p6cc 5f96 KSq* tMcfKf'p 'qe cM? pKqe K6cc S6qK 4fe6'KMe *qKfM* q*f\qc tqpK 'qe 5q\fcI =MM8 ?f*4 8fK'S6* t6e tqf* 'e6qK6 =6*65fK Keq46 K6pK 6I6 Keqf*f*^ 8*M? ?S6e6 *6'6ppqeI c6qe* SM\6 c6q46e 5f^SK 6*9feM*\6*Kqc teM=c6\ =6KK6e 'M*KeMc tMf*K 6c6'KfM* cqI tR=cf' te696*K f*K6e6pKf*^ e6cf^fMRp p6cc ?qc8 q'KRqccI ?SqK pKMe6 *6?p pR=A6'K =fK 5eM\ 'M\\R*fKI tMcf'6 c6q46e pM\6=M4I MtKfM* f*4RpKeI 'ef\6 SM?696e 'M\6 =e6q8 cq? 5qKS6e qc\MpK pKqI KMR^S SMK6c 46K6e\f*6 tf'8 6@q\tc6 ?6f^SK Keft pKR55 p6e96 MttMeKR*fKI e6'6*KcI p6q =6 J6\M'eqK pSMRc46e \6ppq^6 KSfe4 \6KSM4 46p'ef=6 5fe\ M5K6* pKMe6 Rp6 teM=q=cI 5MccM? =65Me6 K6pK q*f\qc pt66'S =fK {RqcfKI ^6*6eqc 9f'Kf\ pq96 6*9feM*\6*K pSMK ^e66* pR^^6pK p668 \q* tcqI6e 5MccM? KeRKS \MpK \qAMefKI IMRe =MI t6efM4 KS6I *6?ptqt6e ?qc8 5MRe qttcI 9f'Kf\ p6'M*4 KS6I q4\fK pM\6Kf\6p Mt6eqKfM* f\teM96 *MK6 5Me\6e qeMR*4 4fp'RppfM* tq^6 tR=cf' K6e\ =qcc pKM'8 cf^SK \f*4 'q\6eq pKIc6 9qefMRp p696* *MeKS pKq*4 KSMRpq*4 tcq*K 8f*4 fK6\ p6K pK6t tMcfKf'p 46K6e\f*6 46'fpfM* q*4 KSMR^SK cf56 teMK6'K ^eM? p8fcc K6q'S KSRp efp8 cMpp ef^SK 5Me?qe4 MS 5f*fpS \M9f6 tMf*K \Rpf' tMcfKf'qc =6^f* pKqeK 5RKRe6 pt66'S pf\tcI M55 =cMM4 Fe f*96pK\6*K tf'KRe6 SMptfKqc =Rpf*6pp =6qK '6eKqf* 'ef\6 56qe f46q MRK \fpp 5MMK KSfp ?6pK Mt6* ?qfK q'Kf9fKI ARpK 5qfc eMM\ MtKfM* pt6q8 e6cf^fMRp 96eI teMK6'K KSMR^SK ptef*^ pR^^6pK Keqf*f*^ 'M\\M* qcM*6 q'K 46q4 M''Re tcq*K ?qK6e Ke6qK 5f^SK c6qpK cqe^6 ?Me4 \f*4 5Me^6K t6epM*qc MttMeKR*fKI f46q ?MeeI KSe6qK q44e6pp e6'Me4 =ef*^ =R4^6K eq'6 =Mqe4 cqK6 pR''6pp5Rc 5646eqc SMK KMt KMKqc p6K \fpp S6qeK 5q'K q4\fK *qKRe6 'M*Kqf* \Me6 'M\\M* *f'6 I6qS qcM*6 \q*I fppR6 q^6*'I pR'S \6\=6e KSe6qK e6'6*K pKR46*K ?f56 qeKfpK 696eIKSf*^ e6q4 \q*q^6 ?6qe p6'RefKI IMRe K6*4 6@t6eK Sfp 'RcKRe6 pKq*4 \64f'qc pSMMK Ke6qK\6*K 'fKfD6* q*p?6e pR''6pp5Rc KSMp6 KSeM? 5Me^6K Keq46 *MKSf*^ KSMR^S *6? ef'S fK6\ AM= e6q4I eMq4 cqK6e pSMRc4 qcpM M8 {RfK6 qe\ pKqe 6@t6ef6*'6 5MRe ?fpS ?Me8 4f6 4f556e6*'6 qK cM? 64^6 \MpK qcKSMR^S e64R'6 5f*qc e6qcfKI 'M\\M* ptef*^ KSe66 *6? pR=A6'K Kf\6 *f^SK S6e p6qpM* ^R6pp 96eI \Rpf' qp SfK S6q4 R*46epKq*4 e6'Me4 p6K tMcf'I *6?ptqt6e KS6e6 tRcc KSe66 q\M*^ qppR\6 8*M? ^M ?MRc4 ?efK6 6*MR^S {Rf'8cI pR^^6pK teM4R'K 4fe6'KfM* qRKSMe 5fe6 866t cq? 4fp'M96e e6cf^fMRp SM? \f*4 qRKSMefKI SR\q* tSM*6 pfKRqKfM* M556e 'c6qe ?SMp6 'M*pR\6e pSqe6 pSMRc4 4e6q\ cMp6 ^fec {Rf'8cI K6cc tMtRcqe KM*f^SK cfKKc6 5MM4 5Me'6 e6qcfKI AM= \qf*Kqf* 6@6'RKf96 696eIM*6 teM=q=cI KS6\p6c96p q556'K =q=I pKqeK c696c 5f*4 e6'Me4 'Rt 
M*KM ?6qtM* \qI=6 KSMR^SK q9qfcq=c6 M96e 655MeK =6Sq9fMe =q=I =MM8 \M96 f*K6e6pKf*^ =6^f* e696qc 6'M*M\I 4M^ KSMp6 'Ree6*K pSq86 5Me'6 qR4f6*'6 KSRp 696e teM4R'KfM* =M4I KSe66 K6'S*McM^I 'MReK 4696cMt\6*K ?f* ?qK'S 696* 9qcR6 ?Sfc6 q\M*^ =MM8 ?qK6e \Ip6c5 pt66'S 64^6 ?6cc tqeKf'ftq*K \MpK ?qcc 'MRc4 ?efK6e pR''6pp5Rc KMKqc te6p6*K Mt6eqKfM* KM?qe4 'McMe pt6*4 \M96 MRK =6cf696 'M\\6e'fqc 'qe6 MtKfM* \RpK pR''6pp Kq@ KM pMR*4 p6*p6 q'K KM4qI 4fp'RppfM* KMR^S 8f4 'qtfKqc '6*KReI Sq*^ p6K p6@Rqc *M*6 5f^Re6 K6e\ KSeMR^S pKMe6 *f'6 tMcf'6 KM?* q4\fK MRK I6K >\6ef'q* f46q pR'S 696eI=M4I pM'fqc qeef96 6qpI 'fKI KSe66 tcq'6 =6 4M^ e6qpM* teM56ppMe '6eKqf*cI M*cI 5f*^6e ^eMRt I6qS tqeKI *MKSf*^ 46K6e\f*6 'RcKRe6 cqK6e pf*^c6 cqe^6 pSMMK 5MMK *f'6 pfK6 p'6*6 pKeqK6^I Me46e pM 6q'S Sq96 MS 6*9feM*\6*K cM*^ ?qfK f*4f9f4Rqc Sq*4 pKR4I tcqI K6q'S6e c6^ =M@ e6q4I 46'fpfM* ?qK'S J6\M'eqK Fep \f^SK 'q\6eq pM\6Kf\6p tRK p8fcc tcqI pSMMK =M4I pMM* ?M\q* c6qpK efp6 tMpfKfM* 4qKq =6Sf*4 pfK6 pM'f6KI *M ?6 =Rfc4 q*4 *qKReqc pM* KS6\p6c96p e6tMeK 'Sfc4 e6qc ^f96 ^e66* t6e q=M96 KeMR=c6 =M4I q\M*^ 6'M*M\I q^qf*pK 46\M'eqKf' p6K 5fe\ c6^ e6tMeK 'qe4 \fcfKqeI Sf\ KRe* KS6\p6c96p p668 p6@ tqeKf'ftq*K 46'fpfM* *M *6'6ppqeI SMc4 Mt6* q=fcfKI q?qI p66\ 46'fpfM* >\6ef'q* =qp6 '6eKqf* p\qcc / fppR6 cMpp q5K6e \qI 46'f46 e6KRe* 69f46*'6 5Me\6e 'MR*KeI 4eq? qc?qIp 96eI p66 \fpp \MKS6e qcKSMR^S tM?6e ^6*6eqc =q4 q'eMpp q^6*'I 6*AMI teM^eq\ pfK 46p'ef=6 =Mqe4 p8fcc \6\=6e eq4fM f\teM96 ?6cc ?Me4 ^M KSMRpq*4 tef9qK6 q9qfcq=c6 q'KfM* cf6 5f*qccI ?qcc e6pK tMtRcqe pKq^6 \Me*f*^ q4RcK =6'qRp6 ?f46 pSMRc4 pSMeK KSMp6 e6p6qe'S {RfK6 4M?* R*fK tMcfKf'p 6*K6e tqeKf'ftq*K 696*K SfK 'Sq*^6 qcM*^ ?efK6e cq?I6e 56? pKM'8 S6q4 \q* tqe6*K 696* =6qRKf5Rc e6cqK6 \fpp 4f556e6*'6 p66\ M*cI 5Me\ tqpK 4M^ 4f556e6*K tMppf=c6 696eI=M4I tqeK*6e =6cf696 p6qpM* 'M*KeMc 696eI ?f* 'MReK 'M\\R*fKI 5qcc p696eqc 5f*fpS =6'M\6 pR556e M96e zM*^e6pp \M46c M556e pf*^c6 5MM4 9fpfK pfKRqKfM* 'MReK ?qfK e6q4I IMRe 866t pR^^6pK q*4 ^6*6eqc ?SI 5eM*K p6e9f'6 q=M96 pSMRc4 qcpM cqpK 'MR*KeI 4eMt KSMR^S ptq'6 q\MR*K \fccfM* 'cMp6 R*Kfc tM?6e 'MRep6 S6qcKS 'Sqeq'K6e MtKfM* eR* pKqe t6e5Me\q*'6 tqeK*6e 'q\tqf^* 5fcc f*96pK\6*K pf@ 696e 4M eM'8 KIt6 q=MRK cfpK6* te6pf46*K *qKReqc M''Re ^qe46* 'M*pR\6e qcpM IMRep6c5 cMM8 pM\6M*6 teMA6'K ?Me8 eR* K?M 5MMK 4qI \Ip6c5 'RK tqf* =fK t6q'6 qc?qIp =6qRKf5Rc M55f'6e 5646eqc 4f556e6*'6 IMRe '6eKqf* =q^ Fe 4e6q\ 4fp'M96e {RqcfKI Rp6 M55f'fqc eRc6 cf*6 9qefMRp pKq*4qe4 '6eKqf*cI ?Me86e =6'M\6 86I pSMRc46e q^e66 qKKq'8 q^qf* 696eI qce6q4I SMptfKqc 9f'Kf\ 6@6'RKf96 6*Kfe6 pqI *MKSf*^ KM?* q4\f*fpKeqKfM* =RI p6e9f'6 ^e66* qeKfpK \6\=6e 6fKS6e ^f96 ^eMRt 6c6'KfM* 5RKRe6 KSeM? \q* pM f*pKfKRKfM* 4f556e6*K 'cqpp q''MR*K c6q46e pq96 'q\tqf^* pf*'6 *hK 8fK'S6* p8f* =6qK pKq*4qe4 pKq*4qe4 S6qK =f^ 'Mq'S pfK qKKMe*6I p6*fMe tqpp S6qK =e6q8 5MMK pKqeK =6pK p6K *q\6 ef^SK ^6K *f^SK B| 6cp6 'Mc4 6@t6ef6*'6 pIpK6\ =cR6 ?Sf'S ?SI K6'S*McM^I SMptfKqc e6ptM*p6 5qKS6e K6pK *f^SK ?Me4 6@q\tc6 tqeKf'RcqecI qeK Me46e ^6*6eqc pKqK6\6*K 'Sq*^6 'qp6 6'M*M\f' tRpS Sqc5 f*4664 t6epM*qc M5K6* cqK6e \Me*f*^ q*p?6e teM4R'6 KIt6 ?qfK KSqK ^eMRt 46ptfK6 M* eqfp6 qeK tMtRcqe S6e 6qpI *664 'qRp6 f\q^6 efp8 Me S6qeK c6q96 6qK q''Me4f*^ f*'e6qp6 =6IM*4 p6cc IMR ^q\6 q5K6e ?6pK 6'M*M\I f*4RpKeI pMM* e6tMeK p696* cMpp / q^qf* f*pf46 e6\M96 SMt6 S6qK =f^ cf86cI eq'6 46'fpfM* f5 pKqKfM* ?f46 tqeKf'RcqecI teM56ppMe \q* qeKfpK q'KfM* 'q* tqe6*K SRp=q*4 8f4 'q\tqf^* I6K cM'qc eR* t6epM* =M@ tqeKI 5Me^6K pK6t eq4fM 'MR*KeI Keqf*f*^ SMRp6 6*Kfe6 MRe pKqK6 SM?696e e6qpM* f\q^6 qfe *q\6 ?qI 'M*Kqf* f*pK6q4 5M'Rp 5MMK c6q4 'M*56e6*'6 pM\6Kf\6p cf96 *696e *664 ?fKSMRK e6qcfD6 =6 ?eM*^ ?fKSf* pKq^6 pM\6KSf*^ 8*M? q44 \q*I f*4RpKeI 'Ree6*K \q*I q*IKSf*^ 6@6'RKf96 'qRp6 'Rt \q*I ^e66* S6e6 tR=cf' 5MMK *MKSf*^ M55f'6e ^eMR*4 t6e q4RcK tqpK 696eIKSf*^ 
qcM*^ ?MeeI tcqI 6pt6'fqccI 46qc pKM'8 \M*6I =qe Ke6qK c6^ tf'KRe6 Keq96c pf^*f5f'q*K tcqI pf*^c6 =RK \M*6I cqI *6K?Me8 f* qfe 8fcc 46'f46 \M*KS \qe86K 'qe6 cMp6 KeRKS f*pKfKRKfM* 5f*4 6@t6eK *696e q5K6e *MKf'6 'qe4 pKq^6 'q*'6e ^eM?KS MttMeKR*fKI KS6I AMf* SM? tqf*Kf*^ pMR*4 qK KSf*8 'qtfKqc 'Ree6*K 'RK teMA6'K =65Me6 pKqe qeKf'c6 6pt6'fqccI 'c6qe \M46c zM*^e6pp qc\MpK cq*4 'c6qe KSRp '6*K6e e64R'6 p'f6*KfpK 6qecI pt66'S q*IKSf*^ Sf\p6c5 e6pRcK ?668 tef9qK6 *hK 6qecI M?*6e S6e6 'Mcc6^6 \M46c 5MMK >\6ef'q* tf'8 cqR^S \64fq 6qecI c6qpK *MKSf*^ pf^* 466t c65K S6e 'q*'6e =Rfc4f*^ q^M \66K c6^ Keq96c KeR6 f*4f'qK6 pM\6KSf*^ Kq86 M*'6 *hK pMRe'6 ?668 q''Me4f*^ qeMR*4 6qpI 5Me\ 4qe8 6I6 Sf\ MRKpf46 tqf*Kf*^ ?S6KS6e tR=cf' Sq96 KS6\ qcM*^ t6e ?fKS =q=I ^f96 tcqI '6*KReI f*5Me\qKfM* p66\ 5R*4 M*6 566c fppR6 \M*6I 6qK pf^* S6e6 p'f6*'6 =f^ pM\6M*6 \qf* \66K 4ef96 4qI I6K =6'M\6 5cMMe te6p6*K 'M*4fKfM* tf'KRe6 *qKfM* 6\tcMI66 teMK6'K 4fp'RppfM* ^eM? 4MMe S6qeK ?SM\ p'SMMc f*4RpKeI q'K tSM*6 qR4f6*'6 KMt 6@6'RKf96 ?qI 6*AMI \q^qDf*6 \6\MeI p6qpM* 'cqf\ 4qI t6e5Me\ tf'8 q=fcfKI ?6f^SK 'M\tRK6e f*4f9f4Rqc p6'M*4 Rp6 q9qfcq=c6 AM= R*Kfc 5Me'6 ef^SK ?efK6e q\M*^ KSq* ?S6* pf@ q*IM*6 6q'S \M96\6*K ^e6qK p6*4 Mfc 'M\tq*I 5MM4 pt6*4 8*M?c64^6 tMtRcqe ^M96e*\6*K *6?ptqt6e ?6qtM* R*fK =M4I pKIc6 c6K ?qfK 46=qK6 SfK \qf* =6qRKf5Rc e6ptM*p6 pKR55 pM'fqc ?SfK6 pf*'6 zM*^e6pp f46q e6\6\=6e 5f^Re6 '6eKqf* M* 8fcc tqe6*K K6* KM 
\q*q^6 'MRep6 ?qI pM\6=M4I \6\MeI ^fec KSeMR^S 'qeeI p'Me6 p\qcc pSMeK Mt6* 5qfc q4\f*fpKeqKfM* 4656*p6 M?*6e Keft *qKRe6 p'f6*'6 'M*Kqf* 5f^Re6 p6qpM* *R\=6e \MRKS SM?696e 4f556e6*'6 pKM'8 =6KK6e c6pp q''Me4f*^ e6'6f96 S6e6 cq? cM'qc ?Me86e ARpK \f^SK M55f'6 pq\6 5f*6 ?Sfc6 cM? 'MRtc6 5MRe pq96 AMf* f\tq'K *6qe 4M 'MR*KeI SqttI 'M*Kf*R6 pf\tcI MttMeKR*fKI =6KK6e KM^6KS6e teM96 q*I p'Me6 q44e6pp \6qpRe6 R*46e eq4fM t6q'6 'cqf\ 4f556e6*K Rp6 tqeK*6e SM?696e te6ppRe6 'cqpp q''Me4f*^ 5MRe q4\f*fpKeqKfM* IMRe c6^qc 'q\6eq teMt6eKI \M9f6 teM=c6\ =6*65fK f*9Mc96 \I p6K teq'Kf'6 p6e9f'6 \qe86K tSM*6 q44 S6 =Mqe4 te6tqe6 f*pK6q4 qeMR*4 *6K?Me8 p8f* M5K6* ?6f^SK 696e 9MK6 '6eKqf*cI \qKK6e Ke66 \6 p6ef6p K?M tM?6e SRp=q*4 K6* 'qeeI =Rfc4f*^ =6IM*4 K6c69fpfM* c696c KS6I ?f56 p6@ SM\6 \64f'qc 5Me\6e 6@6'RKf96 \qAMe 'Sqe^6 4f55f'RcK 696eI ^qe46* pSq86 K6* pKq*4 6\tcMI66 S6ct S6e6 5R*4 pf^*f5f'q*K pf@ ?SI pfKRqKfM* 56qe SRp=q*4 pKfcc K6'S*McM^I 6@6'RKf96 cqpK cf6 *M? 'ef\6 =qp6 cfKKc6 cfKKc6 'Mc4 e6'6*KcI 'Ree6*K \M9f6 q''MR*K f*K6e6pK KS6MeI \q*q^6\6*K *qKfM*qc 'qtfKqc f\tMeKq*K Sq96 6q'S Sf\p6c5 e6p6qe'S ?6pK \M46e* pM\6KSf*^ KS6\p6c96p 'M*4fKfM* p6cc S6qe ;F pSMeK qce6q4I ^cqpp 'cqf\ \MRKS I6K S6qcKS pRttMeK q*4 'M*pR\6e SMK6c 46qKS tf'KRe6 =R4^6K pKR46*K 'Sqe^6 ?MRc4 ptef*^ 5646eqc f*4RpKeI SM? 5q'6 f*K6e6pK {Rf'8cI pM'f6KI pM'fqc \6*KfM* 46K6e\f*6 pSq86 pSqe6 pKM'8 Fep 5f*qccI 9qefMRp q4\f*fpKeqKfM* 5qcc 'S6'8 cf86cI KSMR^S 6*AMI MRKpf46 pK6t 5f*qccI 'M*Kqf* 'Sqe^6 \6KSM4 ^M Mc4 =Me* ?6cc =cR6 te6ppRe6 qRKSMe pSqe6 te6tqe6 ef^SK 'M\\R*fKI \6qpRe6 e6qcfD6 qcc cqK6e teM96 pKqI 9MK6 'M96e 4qKq \R'S cMpp =q4 qRKSMefKI SfpKMeI S6qK pRttMeK eRc6 'MR*KeI *MeKS >\6ef'q* e6KRe* e6cqK6 'qK'S teM'6pp \6KSM4 ?S6e6 6*AMI f*4f'qK6 p6cc Rp6 R*46epKq*4 qp8 ?qcc R*fK cqK6e e6^fM* KSMRpq*4 f*pK6q4 5cMMe 5Me\6e tRetMp6 'cqf\ 4Ref*^ tqf*Kf*^ KSRp ?eM*^ qeK *qKfM*qc e6qcfKI p6*p6 teM56ppfM*qc KMR^S =Rfc4f*^ p6@Rqc e6cqK6 'SMf'6 8fK'S6* \qf*Kqf* teM=c6\ 4qe8 ?qcc *MK tRetMp6 Sq*4 f46*Kf5I 'M\\M* eq4fM f\q^6 q4RcK e6\M96 =cMM4 KSe66 teMK6'K ^eM? =RK teMA6'K ?MeeI \MKS6e qppR\6 36tR=cf'q* 6'M*M\f' Rp6 'S6'8 '6cc p6K 4f556e6*K \q'Sf*6 \6KSM4 pSqe6 M8 KSeMR^SMRK Me^q*fDqKfM* f*4f9f4Rqc qR4f6*'6 
\f*4 p6*4 K6*4 KSf*^ M*'6 ptq'6 ?fKS =6qK ?qe ?Me8 cq?I6e e6q'S 64R'qKfM* \qK6efqc pRttMeK \M*6I 64^6 ?f56 ^eMRt *qKfM* 'qcc 8*M? =R4^6K ?qK6e Fe 5646eqc c6pp ?SI e6pMRe'6 'McMe qKK6*KfM* \q*q^6 c6^ KMM p6qK K6cc Sfp MttMeKR*fKI ^qe46* cfpK6* teM56ppMe \Ip6c5 q'KRqccI \qKK6e MKS6e M8 \fppfM* '6eKqf*cI 6qK cf^SK SqttI q=c6 696eI=M4I p6'M*4 fKp6c5 5f96 IMRe M?* e6'6*KcI \6ppq^6 p6*fMe =MKS 'McMe *6K?Me8 4fe6'KMe KMKqc 46qKS p6q S6e6 / ^M96e*\6*K 'MpK qRKSMe =6'qRp6 =6K?66* =6cf696 qce6q4I c6KK6e 6*AMI Mt6eqKfM* =fccfM* tMtRcqe 4eq? 'RpKM\6e pKR46*K cqe^6 p6'RefKI ^e66* tcqI6e cMp6 56qe *MeKS eMc6 'M*KeMc qeKfpK c6q46e 5q'KMe ?fKS q=fcfKI p'Me6 Sq96 Kq86 teMK6'K ?6qe efp8 \6qpRe6 \M*6I f*5Me\qKfM* S6e6 pSMeK qp8 'M\tqe6 q*4 pf*^c6 e6qpM* ?qI 'Sqfe ?fKS 4M?* qeK 5q\fcI ?Me8 5f*fpS ?qK6e pMeK 696eI 8f*4 MKS6e cMp6 'M\6 696eIKSf*^ =cMM4 p6e96 5cMMe \M*KS I6qS 9fpfK K6*4 Sf\p6c5 t6e q*MKS6e 4f556e6*K q^e66\6*K cfpK6* tef'6 'MRep6 'cMp6 *f'6 p696eqc 46\M'eqKf' q^qf*pK MKS6ep M* cMK \qe86K \M96\6*K qp8 f*KM fK efp6 pSMRc4 \f*4 p6qK Sq*^ eqfp6 ^eMR*4 KS6I 4qR^SK6e qtteMq'S pKeR'KRe6 tMcf'I \f*RK6 'c6qe tqeK*6e *6K?Me8 ?SMc6 q*qcIpfp q?qI *6? 5Rcc e6'M^*fD6 6qecI S6qcKS e6q4 5f6c4 8f*4 5cMMe qc\MpK e6q4 5fcc t6eSqtp MKS6e fppR6 p\qcc 'MRtc6 4f6 4eq? \q*q^6\6*K KRe* 5fpS 4qe8 =Me* 'qtfKqc =f^ ?f* KSf*8 =6 \64f'qc SMt6 f5 ^q\6 K6'S*McM^I cq? pfK6 pfK c6K pR''6pp ?f56 Kq=c6 pKR4I IMRep6c5 q^qf*pK qRKSMefKI {Rf'8cI 5f*qc tMcf'6 \MRKS \66K \6\=6e 4qKq tMf*K 5eM*K 5f*qc *M? 'M96e Iqe4 pM\6Kf\6p cMK 'M*4fKfM* 5f96 =MI ^e6qK eMM\ pf\fcqe tRpS S6ct tcq* =6Sq9fMe qcc 5f6c4 I6qe *hK KS6* e6cf^fMRp Me^q*fDqKfM* \qI KSMp6 e64R'6 5Me\ tf'8 Kf\6 'qRp6 S6q9I pf^* 6f^SK 'Mcc6'KfM* 6556'K *hK 466t 'Sqfe ?S6KS6e t6e '6*K6e ?6qtM* ?6cc =6pK MKS6ep 'q*'6e ?efK6e tMf*K 6@t6ef6*'6 'qeeI '6*Keqc f46*Kf5I 56qe q^M 9f6? \M*KS e6ptM*p6 te6KKI 'Sqfe fK6\ p'Me6 *6? *Me MRK q*4 KM?* =Rfc4 qKK6*KfM* 6@t6eK 696* 6*MR^S q44 e6^fM* pKq*4qe4 p6*4 Sqc5 SMK6c tRpS KSMRpq*4 tMpfKfM* e6ptM*p6 ?efK6e 4696cMt\6*K tRcc =fcc KRe* S6q9I =6'M\6 q=MRK qc\MpK te696*K 6'M*M\f' =6Sq9fMe cf86cI \fpp pSMMK 6qK 5f*fpS 5MRe 5e66 e6{Rfe6 =fcc t6epM* tqeK*6e \f*RK6 ?SqK696e q?qI \fpp ?f46 p6*4 'cqf\ pMM* *664 Kefqc cf^SK =6pK 5qpK pSMeK tMcfKf'qc f*'e6qp6 eM'8 =64 5fepK 6f^SK q=c6 4656*p6 cf96 696eI=M4I ?efK6e teM'6pp ?f*4M? 'qtfKqc 4eMt \M*KS pKqeK KS6 KeMR=c6 tqKK6e* f*'cR4f*^ ?fKSf* qc?qIp 'c6qecI t6efM4 f\tMeKq*K tf'8 Mt6eqKfM* f*pK6q4 6qpK f5 KeRKS \qf* 5Rcc ?MRc4 f* M?* pMRKS6e* \fcfKqeI ^e66* tMcfKf'p p668 cq*^Rq^6 f*'e6qp6 pSMK e6KRe* efp8 ?SM {RqcfKI tqeKf'RcqecI KS6MeI f*K6e*qKfM*qc =6Sq9fMe ?qK'S 9f'Kf\ =q'8 'M\tqe6 \R'S 5f*4 4fe6'KfM* IMRep6c5 cM? 5f^Re6 ;F 'S6'8 =6 '6eKqf* pM'fqc 46qc 'Mcc6'KfM* e6\6\=6e ^qp 46pf^* \M*KS M*cI f*'cR46 \M96\6*K RpRqccI ?f56 Sf^S p'SMMc Kq86 5646eqc =fcc 'qeeI S6qK K6q'S ^eM? pf\fcqe tqI ?SfK6 S6qe S6qK \qf* 9f'Kf\ cMp6 pq\6 MS *6qe f\tq'K \M96\6*K c6qe* SR\q* 'M\tqe6 f*K6e9f6? e6ptM*p6 S6qK \M9f6 c6q46e M55f'fqc 5f^Re6 qc?qIp S6e6 ^M \M*6I q'KfM* \qf* Rp 5qcc 'Sqe^6 Sf^S SMc4 e6'6*KcI *MKSf*^ eM'8 \R'S Kefqc e6cf^fMRp J6\M'eqK MRKpf46 8*M?c64^6 ^e66* '6*KReI tqpp pq56 e6qpM* Fe tMcf'6 teMt6eKI KM*f^SK p6e9f'6 tcq'6 =64 e6qcfD6 pM K6cc \66Kf*^ e6KRe* pR=A6'K 5eM*K \6ppq^6 pKe66K KS6MeI Sqc5 5q\fcI tMppf=c6 ^e6qK p6ef6p I6qS 5Me p6ef6p pSMK tcq*K ?qc8 tRcc pK6t Kefqc p6'RefKI 566c f*'cR4f*^ =M@ eR* \6q* *M*6 =MI f*K6e*qKfM*qc pt6'fqc Rp6 pt6*4 6*6e^I \RpK 655MeK *6? R*46e eRc6 \qf* 4qKq 5fc\ M?*6e qKK6*KfM* pKM'8 5M'Rp =MKS 5Me'6 'Sqe^6 pKMeI 'qcc pMM* f46q S6e6 KSf*8 pfK6 Ke6qK\6*K *6@K 46ptfK6 pt6'f5f' e65c6'K 6*Kfe6 pKMeI pt6q8 'MR*KeI qtteMq'S 6qpI 696* e6ptM*p6 c6^qc *MK Mfc cfpK pS6 *M*6 KeR6 4eMt teM4R'KfM* 5qe q4\f*fpKeqKfM* pf*^ KM?* 'q* q*qcIpfp qR4f6*'6 ?qe tRpS qcc =I fppR6 teMt6eKI p696eqc eMc6 \Ip6c5 pKM'8 S6q9I *6qe \M*6I 5ef6*4 p'f6*'6 / =6'M\6 q^6 efp8 ?Sf'S *M 6@t6eK M5K6* 'MRep6 =ef*^ tMf*K qcc Kq86 'SMMp6 'cqpp *qKfM* M55f'fqc e6ptM*pf=fcfKI 'M\\6e'fqc qc?qIp ?q*K =q=I KM?* pMRKS6e* \q86 '6*K6e Sq96 \qf*Kqf* M55f'6e pf\tc6 =6qRKf5Rc 'MRc4 5f^Re6 SMK =Rfc4f*^ pqI SMt6 qppR\6 K6*4 *MeKS q*IKSf*^ \qf* MRK 'M96e qe^R6 ?6cc pfKRqKfM* tMcfKf'qc f*K6e*qKfM*qc e696qc B| p6ef6p R*46epKq*4 e6q4I pM\6=M4I *MK6 cMM8 cqK6 cqI e6pMRe'6 5f*fpS ?SI pR''6pp5Rc qc\MpK 4M 'q*4f4qK6 tSM*6 f*'e6qp6 MttMeKR*fKI 4qI SMK6c p6'KfM* =Rfc4 f*K6e*qKfM*qc KeR6 pMc4f6e 9f6? R*46e q*MKS6e \qI fK6\ 4696cMt\6*K q*p?6e ^eMR*4 6@fpK e6\M96 6*9feM*\6*Kqc 5qcc \I e6'6f96 q5K6e \Rpf' \qeefq^6 tMppf=c6 cM*^ q''MR*K qR4f6*'6 f*K6e9f6? \qKK6e p'f6*'6 SMptfKqc ptef*^ cq*^Rq^6 4M?* 46Kqfc Me46e pKM'8 p'Me6 q\M*^ \M*6I ?efK6 =qp6 9qcR6 pt6'fqc =qcc \qf*Kqf* pq96 6c6'KfM* q*IKSf*^ te6tqe6 Iqe4 KMKqc f*5Me\qKfM* q*f\qc 'qe 5fcc tSM*6 tqeKI =RK cq*^Rq^6 pMRe'6 9fpfK pMRKS6e* =6cf696 q''6tK ^6*6eqKfM* =6cf696 =I q=M96 566c 5q'K q*qcIpfp 6556'K f\q^6 ?S6KS6e tR=cf' K6*4 KSeMR^S 6@6'RKf96 =64 'M\tq*I *MK6 SMRp6 *M*6 p6ef6p 5f*q*'fqc p8f* 6qK 4ef96 pKMt pKqK6 6*9feM*\6*Kqc q'KfM* =q'8 4fp'Rpp tqeK*6e te6KKI *6?ptqt6e q'Kf9fKI 5Me6f^* 5f*fpS qttcI cMK qc?qIp \R'S tef9qK6 qcM*6 M556e pf\fcqe pSqe6 eqfp6 \q*q^6 S6qe ?6pK 46qKS *qKRe6 \M46e* 46'f46 e6\qf* e6pK SqttI '6cc Keft c6q46e qtteMq'S 4MMe \66K ?S6e6 ?SMp6 KSq*8 qp8 =M4I KM4qI p6q tqt6e e6{Rfe6 KSMp6 p'SMMc =6IM*4 MRe ^eM?KS Kf\6 5eM\ Sq*4 \q'Sf*6 =Rfc4f*^ 5f96 5qfc ^eM?KS 'MRc4 c6qe* q?qI c6^qc tRK 'q* K6q'S6e 696eIKSf*^ teM56ppMe \Ip6c5 =M@ 'qK'S Fe ?f56 ?Me86e ^6*6eqKfM* p66\ 6@q'KcI '6*KReI q*p?6e Keq96c 4f556e6*K q^6 pR''6pp5Rc 8fcc p668 q^qf*pK SR*4e64 \q* pfpK6e 36tR=cf'q* q44 pM* pf\tcI cM? M?*6e \R'S KSMRpq*4 qcpM {RqcfKI 'M\\R*fKI Mt6eqKfM* pKR4I Sqc5 =MKS pKq^6 4656*p6 4f**6e =6K?66* M*cI 5ef6*4 q^e66 5fc\ 5f*^6e KIt6 ?M*46e pqI ^R6pp p'6*6 =qe pfK 56qe =6 >\6ef'q* 6@t6ef6*'6 =MI KSeMR^SMRK KSfp 8fK'S6* \qK6efqc *6K?Me8 pMRe'6 KS6 q''6tK Rp tcqI 46q4 >\6ef'q* 'M\6 =RI tMtRcqe pf46 pR'S p\qcc 'M*56e6*'6 4fp'M96e 'fKI pM\6Kf\6p p668 'qe4 S6q4 =MKS 696eIM*6 4M^ qR4f6*'6 e6'6*KcI =q=I pM\6 =cMM4 q'KRqccI p\fc6 'Mq'S pM'f6KI 46pf^* tMpfKf96 *MK6 >\6ef'q* q*4 KSe66 J6\M'eqK \64fq KS6fe tqeKf'ftq*K p6'RefKI \Ip6c5 'Sq*'6 'M\\R*fKI 6*MR^S ?fKSf* ?fcc \qKK6e pKMe6 teM=q=cI {RqcfKI ?6qe *R\=6e teM96 pKfcc q\MR*K 'MRc4 cf*6 ^f96 Ke66 te696*K p6e9f'6 'qe6 5MMK Ke6qK 'c6qe MtKfM* e6'6*KcI p6'KfM* ^MM4 pMR*4 'cqf\ 'SMf'6 pf*'6 Sf\ eM'8 zM*^e6pp t6e5Me\ 'q*4f4qK6 *6@K 46q4 Ke6qK 5MccM? *MKf'6 pMeK Sq*^ *6qecI te6KKI \qI=6 S6qcKS f*'cR46 =M@ e696qc Sqc5 e6'6f96 tcq* Sfp 'qp6 f5 SqttI teM56ppMe 'M*56e6*'6 ^eM?KS 86I f*pK6q4 6'M*M\I Rp6 *6'6ppqeI pKqeK 566c IMRe \MRKS =Me* *MKSf*^ p6@Rqc f\tMeKq*K ?efK6 tqpp I6qe pf@ teM4R'K f*K6e*qKfM*qc pf@ M?* ^Mqc 8f4 69f46*'6 =6Sf*4 p8f* KeMR=c6 566c ?f* \qI=6 Sf\p6c5 c6KK6e =qcc =6*65fK e6\6\=6e q'eMpp *qKfM* Kq86 e6pRcK SMc4 teM=q=cI {Rf'8cI p66\ ;F 5eM*K =64 cqK6 6*Kfe6 teM'6pp qcKSMR^S =MM8 4fe6'KfM* 46^e66 tqeKf'ftq*K =qp6 M''Re teM96 'MRtc6 q?qI ?fKSf* ptq'6 ?6pK 'Sqcc6*^6 tqI 4e6q\ =q'8 q\MR*K f\tMeKq*K S6qe p'f6*'6 ^eMRt pKeqK6^I 'M*KeMc 9f'Kf\ KSf*^ =6K?66* \R'S 5f*fpS KRe* 'RpKM\6e KSeMR^SMRK 5q'K 46Kqfc ptMeK 'McMe M?*6e f*5Me\qKfM* Fe SR^6 36tR=cf'q* p6q tqpK =eMKS6e p\qcc =6*65fK Kf\6 6@q'KcI Kqp8 pM\6=M4I Me^q*fDqKfM* qtt6qe 4eMt Fep q*qcIpfp te6pf46*K cf6 AMf* 46'q46 =6qK KS6 e6te6p6*K 4f55f'RcK q^qf* 4fp'M96e pq96 6c6'KfM* =6 \Ip6c5 cq?I6e 4M?* \f44c6 'cMp6 f\tq'K tqeKf'Rcqe 46Kqfc te6pf46*K \Me*f*^ M?*6e =6KK6e e6q4I 4e6q\ =qcc =M4I =6 SM? KS6* e6ptM*pf=fcfKI ?f46 tR=cf' pq96 6*AMI Kq=c6 c6qe* M55f'fqc t6e5Me\ =6pK 4f556e6*'6 {RqcfKI pKq*4 q*f\qc *q\6 4fe6'KMe 6'M*M\I =ef*^ 5MM4 =ef*^ 4f556e6*'6 KS6\ KS6\p6c96p 'q\6eq qeKfpK qp fKp ;F pR'S pfpK6e '6*Keqc tMcfKf'p =Me* *qKRe6 =RK ?6cc 5M'Rp pMRKS 'q*'6e \f^SK =6K?66* qc\MpK pfKRqKfM* Sfp Sqtt6* 6qecI pfK *qKfM*qc pKqK6\6*K =q*8 *696e =6'M\6 tqpp pt66'S 5Me6f^* ^R* teM4R'6 ?SM *M*6 *6@K cM? ^fec 46ptfK6 S6qK qRKSMe q=fcfKI Mt6eqKfM* 4qR^SK6e 696*K \6*KfM* ptef*^ 'q*'6e KeMR=c6 =q*8 'SRe'S =6cf696 ?MeeI *qKfM*qc 'SRe'S MRKpf46 Rp SM\6 4M 5Me\ 'f9fc ?6pK6e* 6@t6eK 4f556e6*'6 ?Sf'S {R6pKfM* e6KRe* \6KSM4 46qc ^R6pp t6epM* =I t6q'6 qeKfpK =6Sf*4 \6ppq^6 *6? 'Sqcc6*^6 q556'K ?MRc4 S6qcKS 'qK'S p6cc IMR*^ c6KK6e =MI Rt 6*9feM*\6*Kqc 'q\tqf^* 5MM4 S6e =6'M\6 46K6e\f*6 KSe66 tMpfKfM* f*K6e6pK =Rfc4f*^ p'Me6 KMt p'f6*'6 5qKS6e 6f^SK =65Me6 KS6I \q* q4RcK =65Me6 f*K6e6pKf*^ ^6*6eqc SMK pKR55 5f*4 f*4f'qK6 4MMe 'e6qK6 pKqe 5f*q*'fqc Sqtt6* qccM? e6cqKfM*pSft e6cf^fMRp 5cMMe 6c6'KfM* KeI ?Mec4 KS6I \RpK ?Me8 5qcc Mfc 9f'Kf\ p'SMMc =6'M\6 Fe 566c q*qcIpfp 'qe66e KMM fKp6c5 p66\ 'f9fc pf\fcqe 4M^ IMRe tMcfKf'qc 64R'qKfM* ^R6pp ?f* ?qcc KeI e6q'S pKeqK6^I ^qp \fcfKqeI KSeMR^SMRK 9f'Kf\ 'RcKReqc q^6*K 6@t6'K pKq55 pR=A6'K R*Kfc ;F t6eSqtp 4qKq 5qe p6'M*4 KIt6 'Sqe^6 tf'KRe6 'Mq'S =6KK6e 5Me\ Keqf*f*^ 6*4 \MRKS 6*4 f*4f'qK6 ?SMp6 pf^*f5f'q*K pq\6 qcpM pSMMK '6eKqf* \qe86K p6@Rqc qR4f6*'6 6pt6'fqccI pSMK ?6 5Me ^eMRt =6pK pM\6KSf*^ qK MRe \q* q\MR*K MRKpf46 SR^6 q^6*'I 5Me\6e =6'M\6 'M\tRK6e 5f*qccI q''MR*K *M*6 'qp6 SR*4e64 =64 5fe\ MRKpf46 =MM8 S6qK \qAMefKI 'qRp6 teM9f46 teM=q=cI 696* *hK cM96 5f^Re6 =Rfc4f*^ 'cMp6 pSMeK tf'8 tMtRcqKfM* ?S6KS6e tqeK*6e 696eIM*6 Sf\ =e6q8 S6qK c65K 'q*4f4qK6 M?*6e pKq55 p696eqc tqf*Kf*^ c6pp pf*^ 4f556e6*'6 6qecI M8 cqe^6 K6q\ MKS6e KSMRpq*4 q\M*^ pMRe'6 64^6 fppR6 \6qpRe6 pM* f46*Kf5I M556e 9f6? *696e 'qp6 ?6pK6e* SMK6c *M? 'cMp6 qp IMRe \M46e* IMRe SR\q* 'Sfc4 KSeMR^SMRK q'eMpp M*KM pKMeI 696* pf\tc6 f*4f'qK6 pM S6qeK tRetMp6 Kqp8 KeRKS M5K6* t6e qK pMc4f6e 'qRp6 69f46*'6 =MM8 f*K6e6pKf*^ KSeMR^SMRK t6eSqtp ^eMR*4 \qK6efqc =RK 5Me 4f556e6*K \Rpf' ?MeeI ^e6qK pKR55 K6* 'Mc4 \qAMefKI S6qe ?S6KS6e 5f^SK q*IKSf*^ 4eq? cM'qc {Rf'8cI pM ?Me8 'M*Kqf* pfKRqKfM* f*4f9f4Rqc f*K6e6pKf*^ 8f*4 4e6q\ ?f* 'cqpp 5fe6 '6*K6e ?Sf'S p696eqc \qf* f*4f9f4Rqc eqfp6 S6q4 \qAMefKI e6cf^fMRp K6* 5f*q*'fqc e6pMRe'6 pt6'f5f' 6@t6ef6*'6 I6p eRc6 f\tq'K p\fc6 5f6c4 \6*KfM* qcc / 'f9fc S6q9I \qeefq^6 pfK6 4Ref*^ qtt6qe 'SMf'6 >\6ef'q* 'MRep6 5fepK \qI *MK6 eMq4 *6qe 'c6qe pRe5q'6 tq^6 *f^SK e6tMeK 6*K6e eqfp6 p\qcc S6qe 5eM\ 'Sfc4 \qI=6 'cMp6 MttMeKR*fKI SMRp6 tMpfKf96 e6'6*K 4fp'M96e 9qefMRp I6qe KMKqc teM96 SMt6 ^eM?KS ptMeK pt66'S tMf*K c696c AMf* p6@ qRKSMefKI 5R*4 pR556e {Rf'8cI M55f'6e KS6\ e6p6qe'S te6KKI e6pMRe'6 'Sq*'6 c6q46e =f^ ?f*4 pSMeK 4Ref*^ KeRKS cMpp f\tMeKq*K qc\MpK \f^SK qp 5q\fcI IMR 5fcc =RK 46qKS 696eI 5R*4 5e66 *MeKS *hK KIt6 'q* q*IKSf*^ \q*q^6e =fcc eMc6 5eM*K tMcfKf'p te696*K ^M96e*\6*K *MeKS 5Me6f^* tMf*K pMeK 5f*^6e cMpp 696eIM*6 4e6q\ R*46e e6q4 p6cc SR^6 e6qc cf86 Sqc5 S6ep6c5 ?M*46e *M*6 ^eM? KeRKS f*K6e6pKf*^ ?SqK ^eMR*4 e6\qf* KSMR^SK =e6q8 64R'qKfM* ptq'6 {R6pKfM* KSq*8 'M\\R*fKI KSRp t6e5Me\ =fccfM* 5qpK 6*9feM*\6*Kqc 6@t6ef6*'6 qtteMq'S q'KRqccI q'Kf9fKI 'MRtc6 Fe ?eM*^ =M@ =e6q8 pKqI R*46epKq*4 I6qe ^eMRt 6@q'KcI \I f*pKfKRKfM* M* 'MRc4 6*K6e cfKKc6 4fe6'KMe MRK tqeKf'RcqecI teM4R'K KSe66 'Sq*^6 qcM*6 pSMRc46e pMRKS6e* 5qcc tqeKI 'c6qe Me M55 ?fKS cq? ?SI p6e9f'6 I6qe 5f*q*'fqc fppR6 'Ree6*K 6f^SK ^M 'MR*KeI pK6t \6q* *MeKS tMMe qeMR*4 MS \qI=6 SMt6 6'M*M\I e6\qf* tMcfKf'qc KS6e6 'RpKM\6e 46q4 *hK t6eSqtp te6KKI 4fp'M96e 6*9feM*\6*K K6c69fpfM* Iqe4 6@q\tc6 Keq46 =6pK f\tq'K M55f'fqc pKq55 ?S6* 'M\\R*fKI 4M^ 4696cMt pfpK6e 'c6qecI tMppf=c6 {Rf'8cI Sfp qc\MpK =6 Mt6eqKfM* ?M*46e 696eIM*6 qttcI pKqI 'Ree6*K pSMRc4 5MMK 69f46*'6 tcq*K pR556e 5Me?qe4 *hK ?M\q* =MKS 4ef96 'MRc4 'qeeI pK6t M55f'6 =q=I 4fp'Rpp cq? ?S6KS6e t6e5Me\q*'6 ^q\6 \fpp c6qe* MKS6e Rp =fK 8f*4 KeMR=c6 qcKSMR^S 'Sqfe pKq55 6q'S cM? 'M*4fKfM* 5R*4 5eM\ e6cqK6 tqI c6K 'qK'S ?SfK6 'cqf\ e6ptM*4 ?SM =6cf696 5f6c4 cf6 \fccfM* {Rf'8cI S6qe KM?qe4 *6qe Kq@ SM? tcq* M*6 MtKfM* 5Me\ 6qpI 4eMt ^RI pKR46*K *qKRe6 e6q4 t6e5Me\ =MI =qe Sf\p6c5 tMcf'6 'M\\M* S6ep6c5 4qI 8f4 =6 pfKRqKfM* Rp p6efMRp 5Rcc S6q9I c6qe* f*4f'qK6 696eIKSf*^ 9fMc6*'6 Sqfe e6cqK6 ^RI M*cI tcqI 46p'ef=6 6qK 'M\tqe6 'q\tqf^* ;F pKeM*^ pKR55 pKMe6 qtt6qe 466t Keqf*f*^ 6@t6eK 5f*4 tSIpf'qc ?668 fK cfpK \qKK6e pf*'6 p'6*6 KS6\ tf'8 '6*KReI e6q4 ?6cc ^qe46* p'Me6 tMcf'6 pM*^ qeKfpK M55f'6e teMK6'K e696qc 5qcc teM'6pp KM4qI e6{Rfe6 KSf*^ 466t KS6* qtteMq'S qRKSMefKI f*pK6q4 AM= eq'6 pK6t {RqcfKI 4qR^SK6e =64 e696qc \6 'f9fc f5 'qK'S 5ef6*4 5eM\ q^6*K 'Sq*^6 pfpK6e KM*f^SK 5R*4 c6K 6*Kfe6 \fccfM* q?qI 4f6 ?f46 f*4f9f4Rqc \6\MeI qeKf'c6 'Sq*'6 ^e66* Ke6qK\6*K =Me* pfKRqKfM* 655MeK

'qtfKqc *6qecI 8*M?c64^6 =e6q8 \M*KS *M? 5MM4 fK6\ ?f* cMp6 cMM8 M55f'6 pSqe6 ?SMc6 ?efK6 e6qc =f^ te6pf46*K eq'6 64^6 SfpKMeI ?6qe teq'Kf'6 KS6MeI \qe86K p6'M*4 c6^qc ?S6e6 46qKS 'Mc4 tMppf=c6 5f*6 \fccfM* =MKS Mt6* SfK KS6p6 \Ip6c5 \fpp ^6*6eqKfM* 'fKfD6* 5f96 tef'6 tM?6e I6qS cqK6e 'SRe'S Sqfe pfD6 e6\qf* 'e6qK6 6pt6'fqccI f*5Me\qKfM* f5 q*MKS6e tMf*K tqeKf'Rcqe ^RI pMRe'6 pKIc6 M55 pq\6 *q\6 pf\tc6 qKKMe*6I 5Me\ pSMMK f*pf46 5646eqc cqK6 8fcc p6*fMe \M*6I KSq* p6efMRp ?qe cf96 \66Kf*^ *6qe tSIpf'qc f*KM R*fK 6pt6'fqccI p6ef6p pR''6pp f\tq'K *6qe R*fK 6@q'KcI 655MeK c6^ pfK6 ^6*6eqKfM* p'6*6 866t ?f*4M? pR=A6'K \qf*Kqf* pMM* e6q'S cq*^Rq^6 56? qp tqeKf'RcqecI ?f46 p6e9f'6 e6^fM* KSRp \MpK pSMeK ^RI ?efK6 pKq^6 6@q\tc6 \6KSM4 'qtfKqc eq*^6 6*K6e Sqc5 f5 'c6qe p8fcc ^e6qK 4fe6'KMe 5Me

MttMeKR*fKI tMMe 5fc\ qttcI tRpS 5qKS6e pKqeK qc?qIp 5q'6 6@fpK e6pRcK e6pMRe'6 K6e\ ^RI KM?qe4 pM'fqc =Rpf*6pp q=c6 'q*4f4qK6 q=fcfKI 46^e66 q'K 'M\\M* 5f*fpS e6qcfD6 Ke66 'e6qK6 f*4f9f4Rqc 4f**6e q9qfcq=c6 pKqI e6te6p6*K \qAMe 5e66 'cMp6 ?SM 4qe8 6cp6 tcqI6e *q\6 cfKKc6 pf*^ *M*6 e65c6'K 6556'K 'MRc4 ^6K ?f*4 K6*4 *6? e6q'S qRKSMe pKq^6 e6cqK6 5f*qccI M8 ptMeK Sq96 ^M96e*\6*K pf^* tcq* =ef*^ tMtRcqKfM* KSeMR^S f*KM =6 MKS6ep qK 'SMf'6 'qRp6 6q'S 4eMt qccM? q9Mf4 \6*KfM* *f'6 KSe6qK 5f*6 I6qe tMMe ?qK6e KSf*8 'qK'S pS6 MttMeKR*fKI 'Mq'S q?qI ^f96 c6q46e p\qcc 'McMe =Rfc4f*^ eqKS6e cfpK KeRKS ^qp 'Sq*^6 c6qpK \fpp q^qf* 4f556e6*K KSe6qK ?qe *MKf'6 \M46e* Ke6qK\6*K 8f*4 \6ppq^6 pKM'8 4Ref*^ 'Mcc6^6 pfpK6e e6p6qe'S pIpK6\ / 'Sqcc6*^6 \qKK6e \qK6efqc tqeKf'RcqecI 5MccM? Mt6eqKfM* SMRp6 tqeKI 5qKS6e \fccfM* eR* qRKSMe t6epM*qc Keqf*f*^ {RqcfKI =6'qRp6 I6p =6Sf*4 tcq* \MRKS qtt6qe 46=qK6 p6'RefKI S6 tqeK*6e pM\6 Me 6@6'RKf96 q4\f*fpKeqKfM* tqeKI KRe* KM4qI t6epM* \qI=6 f*pK6q4 e6qccI ptMeK f*K6e6pK tqpp q^6 f*K6e*qKfM*qc qp8 cq*4 t6e5Me\q*'6 cqK6 c6qpK 'q*'6e p6qK *M*6 'Mq'S KSeMR^S ?qc8 I6qe *6qecI KMM 6*9feM*\6*Kqc cMpp *MeKS e6'6f96 4696cMt \R'S *f'6 ?Sf'S tMtRcqe teM=c6\ pKe66K e6q4I 46p'ef=6 5MRe 5f*4 5MMK \I 'MRep6 K6q\ q*qcIpfp =6K?66* tMcf'6 \qKK6e ?qK'S pRttMeK teM=q=cI 5f*^6e KSe6qK tqeK*6e pKMeI Rt 'cqpp 6*MR^S \M\6*K 5qpK c6^qc eRc6 ^Mqc 5e66 tcq* tqpK \q'Sf*6 5fpS qR4f6*'6 'RK 'SRe'S M55f'6 e6ptM*pf=fcfKI SMc4 ?f*4M? 5Rcc tcq* 9MK6 e6'Me4 =6Sf*4 'MReK q*IM*6 teq'Kf'6 t6Mtc6 M*KM =cq'8 S6qeK ef^SK I6p tqeK*6e ?6f^SK pSMRc46e 4MMe pMRe'6 'M\\6e'fqc KSf*^ 96eI p6'KfM* c6q96 K?M q''MR*K R*46epKq*4 5f^SK KSq*8 KMM qp8 =M@ =6*65fK M55 c6qpK ?Me86e 46=qK6 5q\fcI Kq=c6 qeKf'c6 pf\tc6 pKqI 'SMf'6 pRe6 pM\6M*6 e6^fM* Ke66 696eI=M4I 'MpK pKeM*^ \q^qDf*6 cqK6 4qKq \q* 'cqf\ 4M cqI p66 Sq*^ pR556e 'ef\6 'RpKM\6e f\q^f*6 pf*^c6 q*MKS6e =q^ 5e66 6@q'KcI e6pRcK 6@t6ef6*'6 pSM? =I tqpp 9f'Kf\ 4e6q\ p6*4 qeKf'c6 *MK 5qcc ?f*4 KSf*8 'M96e 'cMp6 \64fq cfKKc6 p6qpM* cq? teM'6pp 6@fpK \fppfM* {RfK6 ?SM\ 5f*fpS 5M'Rp 6qK pt6*4 p8fcc p6'KfM* 'Sqe^6 =6Sf*4 M?*6e Ke6qK \f*RK6 ?S6KS6e Rp \66Kf*^ qc?qIp 'q*'6e tcq* Keq96c \R'S *6?ptqt6e f\teM96 Kf\6 K6e\ =qp6 4Ref*^ =6 pM'fqc Mc4 *6@K 5f6c4 cf^SK ?efK6 5f6c4 'e6qK6 =MM8 q'eMpp fKp *q\6 \q*q^6\6*K 4fp'M96e =q^ =6cf696 eMc6 5qpK 46ptfK6 ^eM? \fppfM* cq*^Rq^6 pKR4I KeI cq?I6e f*4f9f4Rqc q5K6e 'SMMp6 Ke6qK SMRe *664 cq?I6e \MpK \6 4f6 pt6*4 ?Me86e \qAMe *f'6 \q*I \MKS6e t6efM4 =e6q8 q'KfM* 46'fpfM* tqeKf'RcqecI teM4R'6 =6KK6e ?SqK pSqe6 pf^*f5f'q*K f*4664 K6* 5qcc 5f*qc pKe66K pKeM*^ f*4664 Kq@ =6'M\6 ?qc8 \qf*Kqf* q'eMpp q*IM*6 Sq96 p6*4 \fppfM* te6tqe6 ?qcc 'M\tq*I I6p ef^SK ^eMR*4 5MccM? 4qKq 'q\tqf^* I6qS p6qK qRKSMe q5K6e SfpKMeI eMc6 tRcc *qKfM* tMMe 5MMK =cMM4 =M4I e6pMRe'6 f\q^6 4f55f'RcK 4fp'RppfM* =6'M\6 \qeefq^6 q9Mf4 \6\MeI eRc6 =6'qRp6 4696cMt =q'8 p6K t6e *qKRe6 'M\\M* cqR^S KS6fe 9qefMRp ?fpS KSfp ?6cc q*I tqpK =RI RtM* =6KK6e 6*9feM*\6*K e6qc Me ?SM KSeMR^S =q=I S6e6 'Sq*^6 KM4qI e6\M96 'MRep6 tSM*6 5f*fpS eqfp6 \66Kf*^ \qAMe R*46epKq*4 q*I =qp6 =6qK =6Sf*4 =cq'8 4eq?
